mpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-68697406.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-68697406.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22H-1B%20cap%20lottery%20results%20roll%20in%20with%20higher%20fees%2C%20new%20procedures%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711765172000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108888907%2Cimgsize-571391.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fnri%2Fus-canada-news%2Fh-1b-cap-lottery-results-roll-in-higher-fees-and-new-procedures-also-kick-in%2Farticleshow%2F108888884.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22LUBNA%20KABLY%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fnri%2Fus-canada-news%2Fh-1b-cap-lottery-results-roll-in-higher-fees-and-new-procedures-also-kick-in%2Farticleshow%2F108888884.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22OpenAI's%20New%20Feature%20Can%20Read%20Text%2C%20Mimic%20Voices%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20is%20sharing%20early%20results%20from%20a%20test%20for%20a%20feature%20that%20can%20read%20words%20aloud%20in%20a%20convincing%20human%20voice%20-%20highlighting%20a%20new%20frontier%20for%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20raising%20the%20spectre%20of%20deepfake%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20sharing%20early%20demos%20and%20use%20cases%20from%20a%20small-scale%20preview%20of%20the%20text-to-speech%20model%2C%20called%20Voice%20Engine%2C%20which%20it%20has%20shared%20with%20about%2010%20developers%20so%20far%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20decided%20against%20a%20wider%20rollout%20of%20the%20feature%2C%20which%20it%20briefed%20reporters%20on%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20OpenAI%20said%20the%20company%20decided%20to%20scale%20back%20the%20release%20after%20receiving%20feedback%20from%20stakeholders%20such%20as%20policymakers%2C%20industry%20experts%2C%20educators%20and%20creatives.%20The%20company%20had%20initially%20planned%20to%20release%20the%20tool%20to%20as%20many%20as%20100%20developers%20through%20an%20application%20process%2C%20according%20to%20the%20earlier%20press%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20recognize%20that%20generating%20speech%20that%20resembles%20people's%20voices%20has%20serious%20risks%2C%20which%20are%20especially%20top%20of%20mind%20in%20an%20election%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20wrote%20in%20a%20blog%20post%20Friday.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20engaging%20with%20US%20and%20international%20partners%20from%20across%20government%2C%20media%2C%20entertainment%2C%20education%2C%20civil%20society%20and%20beyond%20to%20ensure%20we%20are%20incorporating%20their%20feedback%20as%20we%20build.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20AI%20technology%20has%20already%20been%20used%20to%20fake%20voices%20in%20some%20contexts.%20In%20January%2C%20a%20bogus%20but%20realistic-sounding%20phone%20call%20purporting%20to%20be%20from%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20encouraged%20people%20in%20New%20Hampshire%20not%20to%20vote%20in%20the%20primaries%20-%20an%20event%20that%20stoked%20AI%20fears%20ahead%20of%20critical%20global%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20OpenAI's%20previous%20efforts%20at%20generating%20audio%20content%2C%20Voice%20Engine%20can%20create%20speech%20that%20sounds%20like%20individual%20people%2C%20complete%20with%20their%20specific%20cadence%20and%20intonations.%20All%20the%20software%20needs%20is%2015%20seconds%20of%20recorded%20audio%20of%20a%20person%20speaking%20to%20recreate%20their%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20demonstration%20of%20the%20tool%2C%20Bloomberg%20listened%20to%20a%20clip%20of%20OpenAI%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20Sam%20Altman%20briefly%20explaining%20the%20technology%20in%20a%20voice%20that%20sounded%20indistinguishable%20from%20his%20actual%20speech%2C%20but%20was%20entirely%20AI-generated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20the%20right%20audio%20setup%2C%20it's%20basically%20a%20human-caliber%20voice%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jeff%20Harris%2C%20a%20product%20lead%20at%20OpenAI.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20pretty%20impressive%20technical%20quality.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20Harris%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere's%20obviously%20a%20lot%20of%20safety%20delicacy%20around%20the%20ability%20to%20really%20accurately%20mimic%20human%20speech.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnOne%20of%20OpenAI's%20current%20developer%20partners%20using%20the%20tool%2C%20the%20Norman%20Prince%20Neurosciences%20Institute%20at%20the%20not-for-profit%20health%20system%20Lifespan%2C%20is%20using%20technology%20to%20help%20patients%20recover%20their%20voice.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20tool%20was%20used%20to%20restore%20the%20voice%20of%20a%20young%20patient%20who%20lost%20her%20ability%20to%20speak%20clearly%20due%20to%20a%20brain%20tumor%20by%20replicating%20her%20speech%20from%20an%20earlier%20recording%20for%20a%20school%20project%2C%20the%20company%20blog%20post%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20custom%20speech%20model%20can%20also%20translate%20the%20audio%20it%20generates%20into%20different%20languages.%20That%20makes%20it%20useful%20for%20companies%20in%20the%20audio%20business%2C%20like%20Spotify%20Technology%20SA.%20Spotify%20has%20already%20used%20the%20technology%20in%20its%20own%20pilot%20program%20to%20translate%20the%20podcasts%20of%20popular%20hosts%20like%20Lex%20Fridman.%20OpenAI%20also%20touted%20other%20beneficial%20applications%20of%20the%20technology%2C%20such%20as%20creating%20a%20wider%20range%20of%20voices%20for%20educational%20content%20for%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20testing%20program%2C%20OpenAI%20is%20requiring%20its%20partners%20to%20agree%20to%20its%20usage%20policies%2C%20obtain%20consent%20from%20the%20original%20speaker%20before%20using%20their%20voice%2C%20and%20to%20disclose%20to%20listeners%20that%20the%20voices%20they're%20hearing%20are%20AI-generated.%20The%20company%20is%20also%20installing%20an%20inaudible%20audio%20watermark%20to%20allow%20it%20to%20distinguish%20whether%20a%20piece%20of%20audio%20was%20created%20by%20its%20tool.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20deciding%20whether%20to%20release%20the%20feature%20more%20broadly%2C%20OpenAI%20said%20it's%20soliciting%20feedback%20from%20outside%20experts.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20that%20people%20around%20the%20world%20understand%20where%20this%20technology%20is%20headed%2C%20whether%20we%20ultimately%20deploy%20it%20widely%20ourselves%20or%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said%20in%20the%20blog%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20also%20wrote%20that%20it%20hopes%20the%20preview%20of%20its%20software%20%26quot%3Bmotivates%20the%20need%20to%20bolster%20societal%20resilience%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20challenges%20brought%20about%20by%20more%20advanced%20AI%20technologies.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20company%20called%20on%20banks%20to%20phase%20out%20voice%20authentication%20as%20a%20security%20measure%20for%20accessing%20bank%20accounts%20and%20sensitive%20information.%20It's%20also%20seeking%20public%20education%20about%20deceptive%20AI%20content%20and%20more%20development%20of%20techniques%20for%20detecting%20whether%20audio%20content%20is%20real%20or%20AI-generated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711765080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fhtoop18o_openai-unsplash_625x300_16_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fopenais-new-feature-can-read-text-mimic-voices-5337487%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22OpenAI%20is%20sharing%20early%20results%20from%20a%20test%20for%20a%20feature%20that%20can%20read%2