ould%20be%20100%20times%20more%20expensive%20than%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-paying-millions-for-new-data-center-in-wisconsin-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elargest%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20currently%20in%20operation%2C%20per%20the%20report.%20The%20project%20signals%20the%20massive%20amount%20of%20money%20likely%20to%20be%20poured%20into%20the%20industry%20as%20artificial%20intelligence%20continues%20to%20evolve%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStargate%20also%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20far%20exceed%20the%20computing%20power%20currently%20supplied%20by%20Microsoft%20to%20OpenAI%20from%20its%20data%20centers%20around%20the%20country%20but%20would%20require%20at%20least%20several%20gigawatts%20of%20power%20to%20do%20so%2C%20The%20Information%20reported%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft's%20involvement%20in%20the%20project%2C%20however%2C%20hinges%20on%20OpenAI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-launch-better-gpt-5-chatbot-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efulfilling%20its%20promise%20to%20boost%20its%20AI's%20capabilities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20source%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20quest%20to%20obtain%20the%20necessary%20server%20chips%20is%20the%20primary%20factor%20driving%20Stargate's%20hefty%20price%20tag%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%20Finding%20enough%20energy%20sources%20to%20power%20the%20project%20could%20also%20pose%20challenges%2C%20and%20the%20two%20companies%20have%20talked%20about%20possibly%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-plan-to-use-nuclear-energy-power-ai-data-centers-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealternative%20power%20sources%20like%20nuclear%20energy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20demand%20for%20AI%20chips%20has%20reached%20a%20fever%20pitch%2C%20allowing%20a%20select%20few%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20primarily%20%3Ca%20href%3D