0a%20surface%20speed%20of%2027%20knots%20(about%2031%20mph)%20and%20an%20operational%20range%20of%207%2C000%20miles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Languedoc%20features%20a%2076mm%20rapid-fire%20naval%20gun%2C%2016-cell%20vertical%20launch%20system%20for%20surface-to-air%20missiles%2C%20another%2016-cell%20VLS%20for%20cruise%20missiles%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efour%20torpedo%20tubes%2C%20and%20four%20heavy%20machine%20guns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20French%20warship%20is%20also%20capable%20of%20deploying%20with%20rotary-wing%20aircraft%20like%20NHIndustries'%20NH90%20military%20helicopters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFS%20Alsace%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22French%20Navy%20frigate%20FNS%20Alsace%20is%20seen%20in%20the%20background%20as%20a%20CH-148%20Cyclone%20Maritime%20Helicopter%20conducts%20a%20hoist%20exercise%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6607119516bde8d4ead3c49e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFrench%20Navy%20frigate%20FNS%20Alsace%20is%20seen%20in%20the%20background%20as%20a%20CH-148%20Cyclone%20Maritime%20Helicopter%20conducts%20a%20hoist%20exercise%20with%20Royal%20Norwegian%20Navy%20Submarine%20HNoMS%20Utvaer%20in%20the%20Norwegian%20Sea.%3Cp%3ENATO%20Allied%20Maritime%20Command%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Alsace%20joined%20the%20Languedoc%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20earlier%20this%20year%20as%20the%20second%20French%20frigate%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommissioned%20in%20April%202021%2C%20the%20Alsace%20is%20the%20first%20anti-air%20warfare%20variant%20of%20the%20FREMM%20frigates%2C%20which%20include%20FS%20Lorraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20Aquitaine-class%20frigate%2C%20the%20Alsace%20can%20also%20reach%20speeds%20of%20up%20to%2027%20knots%20and%20has%20an%20operational%20range%20of%206%2C000%20nautical%20miles.%20The%20Alsace%20is%20powered%20by%20a%20gas%20turbine%20and%20four%20diesel%20generators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3