2C%20more%20powerful%20setups%2C%20the%20treble%20can%20sometimes%20sound%20thin%2C%20but%20it%20never%20crosses%20over%20to%20sharp%2C%20and%20dialogue%20always%20remained%20clear%20in%20multiple%20test%20scenes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20price%2C%20you're%20getting%20fantastic%20value.%20As%20long%20as%20you%20don't%20mind%20a%20little%20legwork%20up%20front%2C%20the%20V51-H6%20is%20the%20best%20budget%20soundbar%20for%20those%20who%20want%20a%20true%205.1%20system%20without%20breaking%20the%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20compact%20model%5C%22%3EBest%20compact%20model%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20first%20heard%20the%20Sonos%20Ray%2C%20we%20were%20all%20but%20bowled%20over%20by%20its%20audio%20performance.%20Its%20tiny%20frame%20seems%20more%20like%20a%20futuristic%20portable%20Bluetooth%20speaker%20than%20a%20soundbar%20as%20you%20set%20it%20on%20your%20console%2C%20but%20Sonos%20proves%20that%20size%20doesn't%20always%20dictate%20sound.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ray's%20audio%20signature%20is%20full%2C%20clear%2C%20and%20surprisingly%20smooth.%20Details%20pop%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20textural%20sparkle%20that%20borders%20on%20premium.%20Bass%20is%20subtle%2C%20but%20there's%20more%20authority%20than%20you%20might%20expect%20in%20the%20lower%20midrange%2C%20lending%20some%20muscle%20to%20your%20favorite%20action%20flicks%20and%20dramas.%20The%20Ray%20is%20also%20a%20talented%20musical%20companion%2C%20balancing%20everything%20from%20jazz%20to%20electronic%20tracks%20with%20a%20deft%20hand.%20The%20sound%20signature%20occasionally%20obscures%20midrange%20performance%20when%20pushed%20too%20hard%2C%20but%20that%20was%20rarely%20an%20issue%20in%20testing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20white%20Sonos%20Ray%20soundbar%20underneath%20a%20TV%20on%20an%20entertainment%20console.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6607163d16bde8d4ead3c7a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221980%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Sonos%20Ray%20is%20a%20pint-sized%20soundbar%20that's%20perfect%20for%20buyers%20who%20need%20to%20conserve%20space.%3Cp%3ERyan%20Waniata%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bar's%20impressive%20sonic%20skills%20do%20come%20at%20a%20cost%20elsewhere.%20Most%20notably%2C%20there's%20no%20HDMI%20ARC%20connection%2C%20offering%20only%20Optical%20input.%20That%20means%20the%20bar%20can't%20accept%20high-bandwidth%20audio%20signals%20like%20Dolby%20Atmos.%20The%20other%20notable%20drawback%20is%20you%20can't%20automatically%20use%20your%20TV%20remote%20for%20power%20and%20volume%20control%2C%20instead%20relying%20on%20the%20Sonos%20app%20to%20program%20your%20TV%20remote%20for%20IR%20commands.%20This%20is%20all%20the%20more%20complicated%20since%20the%20Ray%20doesn't%20include%20its%20own%20remote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20most%20TV%20remotes%20are%20compatible%2C%20and%20the%20intuitive%20Sonos%20app%20walks%20you%20through%20the%20full%20setup%20process.%20And%20since%20this%20is%20a%20Sonos%20device%2C%20the%20app%20can%20do%20much%20more%2C%20from%20controlling%20the%20bar's%20audio%20and%20settings%20to%20connecting%20it%20with%20other%20Sonos%20speakers%20as%20part%20of%20a%20multi-room%20audio%20system%20or%20a%20full%20surround%20configuration%20%E2%80%94%20something%20virtually%20nothing%20else%20at%20this%20price%20can%20match.%20Sonos%20also%20makes%20music%20streaming%20a%20breeze%2C%20letting%20you%20play%20directly%20from%20the%20app%20itself%2C%20from%20third-party%20apps%20like%20Spotify%20Connect%2C%20or%20via%20Apple%20AirPlay%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20Sonos%20quirk%2C%20there's%20no%20Bluetooth%20on%20board%2C%20but%20WiFi's%20higher%20streaming%20resolution%20and%20the%20swell%20of%20available%20streaming%20options%20mostly%20make%20up%20for%20this%20exclusion.%20The%20Ray's%20unique%20functionality%20takes%20some%20getting%20used%20to%2C%20and%20it%20won't%20be%20for%20everyone.%20But%20this%20mini%20bar's%20killer%20sound%20and%20advanced%20features%20make%20it%20an%20excellent%20value%20proposition%20for%20the%20right%20buyer%2C%20especially%20for%20those%20already%20invested%20in%20the%20Sonos%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20test%20budget%20soundbars%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20test%20budget%20soundbars%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Vizio%20M%20Series%205.1%20soundbar%20on%20an%20entertainment%20console%20under%20a%20TV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6607166d1caec1275a6b06e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20evaluate%20soundbars%20using%20an%20assortment%20of%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows.%3Cp%3ERyan%20Waniata%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20the%20best%20budget%20soundbars%2C%20we%20tested%20multiple%20models%20for%20several%20hours%20each%20in%20various%20use%20cases.%20Our%20biggest%20focus%20is%20always%20sound%20quality%2C%20but%20we%20also%20weigh%20supported%20audio%20formats%2C%20connectivity%2C%20ease%20of%20use%2C%20and%20advanced%20features%20like%20WiFi%20streaming%20and%20smart%20assistant%20compatibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20evaluate%20factors%20for%20daily%20use%2C%20from%20setup%20and%20size%20to%20reliability%20and%20convenience%20perks%20like%20an%20app%20for%20adjusting%20EQ%20and%20other%20settings.%20As%20often%20as%20possible%2C%20we%20live%20with%20each%20soundbar%20for%20multiple%20days%2C%20using%20it%20in%20various%20scenarios%20as%20our%20main%20audio%20device%20to%20find%20out%20what%20it's%20truly%20like%20to%20own%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20testing%20material%2C%20we%20use%20a%20carefully%20selected%20list%20of%20scenes%20from%20familiar%20films%20and%20TV%20shows.%20We%20look%20for%20a%20well-blended%20system%20across%20bass%2C%20midrange%2C%20and%20treble%20frequencies%2C%20as%20well%20as%20paying%20careful%20attention%20to%20dialogue%20delivery%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20when%20things%20get%20chaotic%2C%20but%20also%20during%20quiet%20moments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20listen%20to%20a%20dedicated%20song%20list%20of%20tracks%20from%20multiple%20music%20genres%20and%20streaming%20services%2C%20including%20Spotify%20and%20high-resolution%20files%20over%20services%20like%20Amazon%20Music.%20We%20make%20sure%20to%20test%20each%20system%20for%20Bluetooth%20and%20WiFi%20reliability%20and%20audio%20quality%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20responsiveness%20and%20convenience%20of%20smart%20assistants%20like%20Amazon%20Alexa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20budget%20soundbar%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20budget%20soundbar%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Bose%20Smart%20Soundbar%20600%20inputs%20shown%20on%20a%20wooden%20console.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6455555e02f891001861a905%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou'll%20want%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20soundbar%20you%20buy%20has%20all%20the%20inputs%20you%20need%20to%20connect%20to%20your%20devices.%3Cp%3ERyan%20Waniata%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20shopping%20for%20the%20best%20budget%20soundbar%2C%20you'll%20first%20want%20to%20look%20at%20connectivity.%20HDMI%20ARC%20or%20eARC%20are%20preferred%20for%20connection%20to%20a%20TV%2C%20as%20they%20offer%20higher%20bandwidth%20than%20digital%20optical%20connection%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20passing%20of%20CEC%20(Consumer%20Electronics%20Control)%20from%20most%20modern%20TVs%2C%20letting%20you%20use%20your%20TV%20remote%20to%20control%20basic%20controls%20like%20power%20and%20volume.%20For%20music%20streaming%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20decide%20if%20you%20need%20WiFi%20support%20or%20if%20Bluetooth%20will%20suffice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20we%20recommend%20looking%20at%20available%20audio%20channels.%20Many%20budget%20models%20will%20be%20limited%20to%202.0%20(stereo%20audio)%20or%202.1%20channel%20configurations%20(which%20include%20a%20low-frequency%20channel%20or%20separate%20subwoofer%20for%20bass).%20Some%20newer%20models%20go%20further%2C%20with%20support%20for%20an%20integrated%20center%20channel%2C%20which%20is%20denoted%20with%20a%203.0%20or%203.1-channel%20configuration%2C%20or%20even%205.1-channel%20surround%20with%20satellite%20speakers.%20Moving%20up%20in%20price%20can%20get%20you%20into%20soundbars%20with%20Dolby%20Atmos%20support.%20Bose's%20Smart%20Soundbar%20600%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20supports%203.0.2%20channel%20sound%2C%20which%20means%20it%20offers%20three%20front%20channels%20as%20well%20as%20two%20%26quot%3Bheight%26quot%3B%20channels%20to%20create%20a%20more%20immersive%20soundstage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegarding%20audio%20formats%2C%20many%20budget%20soundbars%20will%20support%20both%20PCM%20and%20Dolby%20Digital%20stereo%20sound%20as%20a%20baseline%2C%20while%20some%20go%20further%2C%20including%20DTS%20and%20DTS%20surround%20sound.%20Many%20of%20the%20best%20budget%20soundbars%20we%20test%20also%20include%20virtual%20surround%20sound%20formats%20like%20DTS%20Virtual%20X%2C%20which%20uses%20digital%20software%20to%20create%20a%20more%20immersive%20experience.%20This%20can%20offer%20a%20notable%20soundstage%20expansion%20but%20won't%20be%20as%20effective%20as%20true%20multi-channel%20surround%20sound%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoundbars%20are%20also%20great%20for%20streaming%20music.%20The%20vast%20majority%20of%20budget%20soundbars%20offer%20at%20least%20some%20form%20of%20Bluetooth%20support%20to%20stream%20from%20your%20phone%2C%20while%20more%20advanced%20models%20include%20WiFi%20connectivity%20for%20streaming%20at%20higher%20quality%20from%20services%20like%20Spotify%20or%20Apple%20Music.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWiFi%20connectivity%20may%20also%20enable