ou%20want.%20Our%20top%20pick%20for%20this%20guide%20costs%20just%20over%20%24100%2C%20which%20we%20consider%20the%20baseline%20when%20shopping%20for%20the%20best%20budget%20soundbars.%20If%20you're%20picky%20about%20sound%2C%20however%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20consider%20investing%20at%20least%20%24200-300%20for%20a%20more%20immersive%20and%20engaging%20experience.%20If%20you%20want%20more%20advanced%20features%20and%20support%20for%20sound%20formats%20like%20Dolby%20Atmos%2C%20expect%20to%20spend%20even%20more%2C%20but%20you%20can%20still%20get%20a%20great%20experience%20for%20under%20%24500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20budget%20soundbars%20support%20surround%20sound%20and%20Dolby%20Atmos%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYes.%20We%20included%20budget-friendly%20soundbar%20models%20on%20our%20list%20with%20surround%20sound%20and%20Dolby%20Atmos%20support.%20One%20thing%20to%20note%20is%20that%20while%20budget%20Dolby%20Atmos%20soundbars%20can%20offer%20a%20height%20element%20for%20a%20more%20immersive%20experience%2C%20without%20true%20surround%20speakers%2C%20these%20models%20may%20not%20be%20as%20immersive%20as%20soundbars%20that%20include%20rear%20satellites.%20For%20more%20information%2C%20check%20out%20our%20guide%20to%20all%20the%20ins%20and%20outs%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-dolby-atmos%5C%22%3EDolby%20Atmos%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20if%20you're%20after%205.1%20surround%20sound%20or%20higher%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20invest%20not%20only%20in%20a%20soundbar%20that%20supports%20these%20features%20but%20also%20in%20a%20dedicated%20space%20to%20properly%20place%20surround%20sound%20speakers%20so%20that%20they're%20aligned%20with%20your%20main%20listening%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20our%20experience%2C%20a%20budget%20surround%20soundbar%20is%20a%20great%20way%20to%20determine%20if%20a%20multi-speaker%20system%20is%20your%20preferred%20listening%20exper