ive%20anything%20from%20Lufthansa%2C%20though%20Giantisco%20did%20receive%2044%2C000%20miles%20from%20United%20%E2%80%94%20valued%20at%20%24528%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nerdwallet.com%2Farticle%2Ftravel%2Fcalculator-should-you-book-a-flight-with-cash-or-miles%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENerd%20Wallet%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20week%20after%20BI%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20airline%20for%20comment%20on%20March%2011.%20Marton%20hasn't%20received%20any%20miles%20or%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELufthansa%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMore%20than%20anything%2C%20we%20need%20the%20money%20we%20spent%20trying%20to%20get%20home%20at%20the%20last%20minute%20and%20being%20stuck%20in%20Munich%2C%26quot%3B%20Giantisco%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223264%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lufthansa%20plane%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c7bb7a917a1dae0245458b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222262%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Lufthansa%20aircraft%20on%20a%20tarmac.%20%3Cp%3ENurPhoto%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBad%20weather%20and%20technology%20landed%20the%20couple%20in%20this%20situation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20traveling%20around%20Southeast%20Asia%20for%20two%20months%20last%20summer%2C%20the%20couple%20embarked%20on%20a%20trip%20back%20home%20to%20Lambertville%2C%20New%20Jersey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20booked%20their%20return%20flight%20months%20in%20advance%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-redeem-credit-card-points-for-travel-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnited%20using%20miles%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Their%20scheduled%20flight%20would%20take%20them%20on%20a%20United%20plane%20from%20Singapore%20to%20Munich.%20In%20Munich%2C%20they'd%20board%20United's%20partner%20airline%2C%20Lufthansa%2C%20for%20a%20flight%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20made%20it%20to%20Germany%20and%20boarded%20their%20connecting%20flight.%20But%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faviation-experts-why-its-a-nightmare-to-fly-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebad%20weather%20delayed%20the%20departure%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20the%20crew%20timed%20out%2C%20the%20flight%20was%20canceled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Giantisco%20remembers%20thinking%20they'd%20easily%20be%20rebooked%20on%20the%20next%20flight%20to%20New%20Jersey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20contacted%20Lufthansa's%20customer%20service%20department%2C%20where%20a%20representative%20told%20them%20the%20next%20available%20flight%20wasn't%20for%20two%20days.%20The%20couple%20agreed%20to%20the%20rebooking%20since%20that%20was%20the%20only%20option%20offered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20trouble%20started.%20Later%2C%20when%20the%20couple%20opened%20their%20Lufthansa%20and%20United%20accounts%2C%20there%20weren't%20any%20upcoming%20reservations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiantisco%20called%20United%2C%20and%20a%20representative%20attempted%20to%20rebook%20them%20on%20two%20separate%20flights%20home%20%E2%80%94%20different%20from%20their%20Lufthansa%20rebooking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20reservation%20was%20deleted%20from%20their%20account%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiantisco%20said%20it%20spiraled%20into%20a%20situation%20where%20both%20airlines%20blamed%20the%20other.%20Reservations%20would%20be%20made%20over%20the%20phone%20but%20disappear%20from%20their%20accounts%20hours%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20sent%20to%20BI%20at%20the%20time%2C%20a%20Lufthansa%20representative%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bafter%20the%20original%20onward%20flight%20LH412%20from%20Munich%20to%20Newark%20was%20canceled%20on%20August%2017%2C%20Lufthansa%20immediately%20booked%20an%20alternative%20train%20from%20Munich%20to%20Frankfurt%20and%20a%20flight%20from%20Munich%20to%20Newark%20for%20August%2019%2C%20which%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20was%20deleted%20by%20United%20Airlines.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnited%20told%20BI%20that%20%26quot%3Bafter%20receiving%20a%20new%20itinerary%20from%20their%20canceled%20Lufthansa%20flight%2C%20the%20customer%20called%20United%20to%20explore%20their%20options%2C%20and%20we%20rebooked%20them%20on%20a%20new%20flight%20the%20following%20day.%20When%20the%20customers%20did%20not%20show%20up%20for%20this%20flight%2C%20they%20reached%20out%20to%20Lufthansa%20instead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiantisco%20and%20Marton%20said%20that's%20far%20from%20what%20happened.%20Instead%2C%20they%20longed%20to%20get%20home%2C%20but%20with%20no%20active%20reservations%20on%20their%20accounts%2C%20there%20was%20no%20way%20to%20board%20the%20flights%20and%20trains%20the%20airlines%20claimed%20to%20have%20booked%20them%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20time%2C%20we%20went%20to%20the%20airport%2C%20but%20we%20had%20no%20way%20to%20check%20into%20the%20flight%20or%20any%20way%20to%20say%20that%20we%20were%20on%20the%20flight%20because%20they%20deleted%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20Giantisco%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarton%20said%20after%20the%20sixth%20or%20seventh%20failed%20rebooking%2C%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20heart-sinking%20feeling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20more%20it%20happened%20at%20later%20and%20later%20dates%2C%20it%20just%20felt%20more%20and%20more%20like%20we%20were%20never%20going%20to%20get%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feuropa.eu%2Fyoureurope%2Fcitizens%2Ftravel%2Fpassenger-rights%2Fair%2Findex_en.htm%23reimbursement-cancellation-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEuropean%20Union%20air%20passenger%20rights%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20airline%20passengers%20can%20choose%20between%20a%20reimbursement%2C%20rerouting%2C%20or%20return%20if%20their%20flight%20is%20canceled.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20Gianstico%20and%20Marton%20chose%20to%20be%20rerouted%2C%20which%20requires%20the%20airline%20to%20book%20tickets%20at%20%26quot%3Bthe%20earliest%20opportunity.%26quot%3B%20Giantisco%20said%20the%20airline%20failed%20that%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20after%20three%20days%20in%20Munich%2C%20the%20couple%20gave%20up%20on%20rebooking%20and%20purchased%20new%20tickets%20with%20United%20Airlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20flew%20from%20Munich%20to%20London%20on%20a%20Lufthansa%20flight%20and%20from%20London%20to%20New%20Jersey%20on%20United.%20The%20tickets%20cost%20%243%2C153.50.%20Adding%20in%20costs%20for%20hotels%2C%20food%2C%20local%20transportation%2C%20and%20clothing%20%E2%80%94%20the%20airlines%20lost%20their%20luggage%2C%20too%20%E2%80%94%20the%20couple%20said%20they%20spent%20%244%2C430.79.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Emma%20Giantisco%20and%20Dylan%20Marton%20on%20their%20two-month%20trip.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f0f8b05114270019aec022%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEmma%20Giantisco%20and%20Dylan%20Marton%20on%20their%20two-month%20trip.%3Cp%3EEmma%20Giantisco%20and%20Dylan%20Marton%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnited%20refunded%20the%20couple%20%2482%20and%20issued%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGiantisco%3Cstrong%3E%20miles%20months%20later%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20home%2C%20Marton%20and%20Giantisco%20were%20determined%20to%20get%20their%20money%20back.%20That%20became%20a%20challenge%20when%20they%20discovered%20their%20original%20flight%20information%20had%20been%20removed%20from%20their%20United%20flight%20history.%20BI%20viewed%20more%20than%2015%20pages%20of%20screenshots%20the%20couple%20took%20throughout%20their%20attempted%20rebooking%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20contacted%20both%20airlines%2C%20unsure%20which%20airline%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20reimbursement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20received%20a%20refund%20of%20%2482%20from%20United%20for%20the%20clothes%20they%20purchased%20in%20the%20US%20once%20they%20arrived%20home%20without%20their%20luggage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20email%20sent%20to%20Gianstico%2C%20a%20United%20representative%20said%20the%20Star%20Alliance%20partnership%20agreement%20states%20that%20the%20operating%20carrier%20is%20responsible%20for%20refunds%20after%20a%20canceled%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20Lufthansa%20denied%20the%20refund%2C%20but%20the%20couple%20pushed%20back.%20In%20October%2C%20the%20airline%20sent%20them%20an%20email%2C%20viewed%20by%20BI%2C%20that%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20would%20like%20to%20offer%20you%20a%20refund%20for%20the%20tickets%20you%20still%20have%20open.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20is%20unaware%20of%20any%20tickets%20they%20have%20open%20with%20the%20airline%20or%20how%20much%20that%20refund%20would%20be.%20They%20haven't%20received%20money%20from%20Lufthansa%20since%20the%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20sent%20to%20BI%20in%20mid-March%2C%20a%20United%20representative%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20goodwill%20gesture%2C%20we%20reimbursed%20some%20expenses%20from%20their%20unexpected%20overnight%20stay%20and%20are%20working%20with%20Lufthansa%20to%20refund%20the%20miles%20used%20for%20the%20canceled%20flight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20week%20later%2C%20Giantisco%20received%2044%2C000%20miles%20in%20her%20United%20account.%20But%20Gianstico%20and%20Marton%20agree%20that%20the%20miles%20don't%20begin%20to%20help%20the%20%244%2C430%20missing%20from%20their%20bank%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20of%20us%20work%20in%20education%2C%20so%20we're%20a%20solid%20middle-class%20household.%20I%20would%20say%20this%20is%20the%20first%20year%20that%20I've%20felt%20a%20lot%20of%20stress%20about%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Giantisco%20said.%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20these%20strains%20would%20have%20felt%20more%20manageable%20if%20not%20for%20this%20loss%20of%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20believe%20that%20the%20airlines%20need%20to%20take%20accountability%20for%20what%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20there's%20any%20other%20sort%20of%20company%20or%20sector%20that%20can%20promise%20a%20service%2C%20cancel%20the%20service%2C%20strand%20you%2C%20promise%20to%20repay%20you%2C%20and%20then%20ghost%20you%20for%207%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20Giantisco%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20unfathomable%20behavior.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20travel%20nightmare%20to%20share%3F%20Business%20Insider%20would%20like%20to%20hear%20from%20you.%20Email%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Amhumphries%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Emhumphries%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-says-lufthansa-promised-refund-for-canceled-flight-hasnt-delivered-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711748707000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f0f8b157bff70019480095%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-says-lufthansa-promised-refund-for-canceled-flight-hasnt-delivered-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lufthansa%20canceled%20a%20couple's%20flight%20last%20summer.%20They're%20still%20awaiting%20a%20refund%20from%20the%20airline%20despite%20being%20told%20they%20would%20get%20one%20in%20October.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mhumphries%40businessinsider.com%20(Monica%20Humphries)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A51%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-says-lufthansa-promised-refund-for-canceled-flight-hasnt-delivered-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%226%20get%20life%20for%20murder%20of%20BSP%20MLA%20plotted%20by%20Atiq%2C%20brother%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711748649000%2C%22visual%