%20easy-to-apply%2C%20lightly%20scented%20shampoo%20that%20cleans%20and%20deodorizes%20without%20drying%20the%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20shampoo%20for%20puppies%20and%20adult%20dogs%20contains%20a%20proprietary%20natural%20enzyme%20blend%20that%20provides%20a%20deep%20clean%20by%20removing%20the%20residues%20of%20protein%2C%20fat%2C%20and%20starch%20from%20a%20dog's%20fur%20and%20skin.%20It%20also%20contains%20naturally%20occurring%20biosurfactants%2C%20which%20are%20produced%20by%20microbes%20and%20boost%20the%20shampoo's%20cleaning%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20available%20in%20four%20natural%2C%20essential%20oil-based%20fragrances%3A%20lavender%2C%20citrus%2C%20oatmeal%20mango%2C%20and%20tea%20tree.%20The%20ingredients%20are%20biodegradable%2C%20making%20it%20a%20safe%20choice%20for%20dogs%20and%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shampoo%20distributes%20quickly%20and%20easily%20across%20a%20dog's%20skin%20and%20coat%20and%20doesn't%20leave%20any%20residue%20after%20it's%20wiped%20off%20with%20a%20towel.%20For%20the%20face%2C%20the%20manufacturer%20recommends%20spraying%20the%20shampoo%20on%20a%20damp%20cloth%20first%20and%20then%20gently%20rubbing%20the%20face%2C%20carefully%20avoiding%20a%20dog's%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWaterless%20shampoos%20are%20often%20helpful%20in%20specific%20situations%2C%20such%20as%20after%20surgery%20when%20a%20dog's%20incision%20site%20has%20to%20stay%20dry%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr.%20Cherese%20Sullivan%2C%20a%20relief%20veterinarian%20in%20Houston%2C%20Texas.%20Dogs%20that%20suffer%20from%20incontinence%20or%20don't%20like%20being%20bathed%20can%20also%20benefit%20from%20the%20quick%20cleaning%20provided%20by%20a%20waterless%20shampoo.%20These%20shampoos%20are%20also%20a%20good%20option%20when%20there's%20a%20long%20time%20between%20grooming%20appointments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBe%20mindful%20that%20waterless%20shampoos%20might%20not%20provide%20the%20same%20level%20of%20cleaning%20that%20a%20bath%20with%20one%20of%20the%20best%20dog%20shampoos%20can%20provide.%20Todd-Jenkins%20says%20bathing%20a%20dog%20with%20water%20and%20shampoo%20does%20a%20superior%20job%20of%20mechanically%20removing%20dirt%20and%20debris%20from%20the%20fur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20puppies%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20puppies%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20other%20puppy%20shampoos%20we%20considered%20that%20contained%20synthetic%20ingredients%2C%20Earthbath%20Ultra-Mild%20Puppy%20Shampoo%20uses%20natural%20ingredients%20to%20clean%2C%20condition%2C%20and%20detangle%2C%20making%20it%20our%20top%20choice%20among%20the%20best%20dog%20shampoos%20for%20puppies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20puppy's%20skin%20is%20more%20sensitive%20than%20an%20adult%20dog's%20skin.%20Because%20of%20this%2C%20puppy%20shampoos%20are%20formulated%20to%20be%20extra-gentle%20while%20still%20being%20effective%20at%20cleaning%20and%20moisturizing%20the%20skin%20and%20coat.%20This%20shampoo%20contains%20ingredients%20such%20as%20aloe%20vera%20and%20various%20vitamins%20to%20moisturize%20and%20nourish%20a%20puppy's%20skin%20and%20coat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shampoo%20is%20safe%20for%20puppies%20at%20least%206%20weeks%20of%20age%20and%20does%20not%20wash%20off%20topical%20flea%20and%20tick%20treatments.%20For%20the%20first%20few%20weeks%20of%20life%2C%20puppies%20have%20trouble%20regulating%20their%20body%20temperature%20so%20they%20can%20get%20cold%20easily.%20Because%20of%20this%2C%20it%20is%20recommended%20that%20puppies%20not%20be%20bathed%20until%20they%20are%20at%20least%206%20to%208%20weeks%20old%20when%20they're%20better%20at%20regulating%20their%20body%20temperature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarthbath%20Ultra-Mild%20Puppy%20Shampoo%20lathers%20well%20and%20rinses%20easily%2C%20which%20helps%20if%20you%20have%20a%20squirmy%20puppy%20that%20doesn't%20like%20to%20hold%20still%20for%20a%20long%20bath.%20The%20gentle%2C%20tear-free%20formula%20will%20not%20sting%20a%20puppy's%20eyes%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20take%20extra%20care%20to%20avoid%20the%20eyes%2C%20nose%2C%20and%20mouth%20when%20bathing%20a%20dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20whitening%5C%22%3EBest%20whitening%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDogs%20with%20white%20fur%20need%20more%20than%20just%20regular%20shampoo.%20They%20need%20a%20shampoo%20that%20also%20removes%20discoloring%20stains%2C%20like%20urine%20and%20food%2C%20that%20are%20more%20obvious%20on%20white%20coats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChris%20Christensen%20White%20on%20White%20Shampoo%20for%20Pets%20whitens%20and%20brightens%20a%20dog's%20fur%20for%20four%20weeks%20without%20relying%20on%20harsh%20chemicals%20like%20bleaching%20agents.%20It%20also%20removes%20yellow%20stains%20and%20provides%20a%20deep%20clean.%20As%20a%20bonus%2C%20the%20shampoo%20can%20be%20used%20on%20dogs%20with%20any%20coat%20color%20to%20increase%20the%20fur's%20luster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhitening%20shampoos%20are%20primarily%20classified%20as%20bluing%2C%20enzymatic%2C%20or%20clarifying.%20Bluing%20shampoos%2C%20also%20called%20optical%20brighteners%2C%20contain%20blue%20or%20purple%20color%20enhancers%20that%20absorb%20and%20reflect%20light%20to%20hide%20stains.%20Enzymatic%20shampoos%20break%20down%20proteins%20that%20cause%20discoloration.%20Clarifying%20shampoos%20strip%20dirt%20from%20the%20hair%20cuticles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20shampoo%20has%20a%20purple%20color%20that%20provides%20an%20optical%20brightening%20effect.%20It%20should%20be%20left%20on%20for%20up%20to%2010%20minutes%3B%20if%20left%20on%20longer%2C%20it%20may%20leave%20a%20slight%20purple%20tint%20on%20the%20fur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20shampoo's%20formula%20is%20gentle%2C%20the%20manufacturer%20recommends%20testing%20the%20shampoo%20in%20a%20small%20skin%20area%20if%20a%20dog%20has%20allergies.%20It%20is%20safe%20for%20puppies%20at%20least%2016%20weeks%20of%20age%20and%20adult%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20dog%20shampoo%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20shopping%20for%20a%20dog%20shampoo%2C%20there%20are%20several%20things%20to%20keep%20in%20mind.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIngredients%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Look%20for%20shampoos%20that%20contain%20100%25%2C%20or%20nearly%20100%25%2C%20natural%20ingredients.%20These%20ingredients%20are%20less%20likely%20to%20cause%20irritation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAge%20and%20safety%20for%20puppies%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Make%20sure%20the%20shampoo%20you%20use%20is%20labeled%20for%20your%20dog's%20age.%20If%20a%20recommended%20age%20isn't%20clearly%20stated%20on%20the%20label%2C%20we%20recommend%20contacting%20the%20manufacturer%20for%20the%20information.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EScent%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Natural%2C%20light%20fragrances%20are%20best.%20This%20ensures%20both%20you%20and%20your%20dog%20aren't%20put%20off%20by%20powerful%20scents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPurpose%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EShampoos%20are%20formulated%20for%20specific%20needs.%20A%20simple%20cleansing%20and%20moisturizing%20shampoo%2C%20like%20our%20top%20pick%2C%20is%20suitable%20for%20most%20dogs.%20But%20if%20you're%20looking%20to%20prevent%20and%20treat%20fleas%2C%20brighten%20your%20dog's%20white%20coat%2C%20or%20treat%20a%20particular%20skin%20condition%2C%20the%20shampoo%20should%20be%20labeled%20for%20that%20use.%20If%20your%20dog%20has%20a%20skin%20condition%2C%20it's%20best%20to%20check%20with%20your%20veterinarian%20before%20choosing%20a%20shampoo.%20For%20certain%20conditions%2C%20they%20may%20recommend%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-medicated-shampoo-for-dogs%5C%22%3Ebest%20medicated%20dog%20shampoos%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20selected%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20selected%20the%20best%20dog%20shampoos%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20consulted%20with%20two%20veterinarians%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20dog%20shampoos.%20While%20they%20didn't%20provide%20specific%20recommendations%2C%20they%20shared%20their%20clinical%20expertise%20regarding%20how%20dog%20shampoos%20can%20be%20used%20for%20different%20purposes.%20We%20also%20researched%20how%20dog%20shampoos%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20selection%20criteria%20that%20we%20used%20to%20evaluate%20the%20best%20dog%20shampoos%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIngredients%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20analyzed%20the%20ingredients%20list%20of%20each%20shampoo%20to%20identify%20natural%20and%20synthetic%20ingredients.%20Preference%20was%20given%20to%20shampoos%20that%20contained%20natural%20ingredients%20that%20are%20gentle%20on%20a%20dog's%20skin.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAge%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0Except%20for%20puppy%20shampoos%2C%20shampoos%20were%20rated%20higher%20if%20they%20were%20safe%20for%20puppies%20and%20adult%20dogs.%20They%20were%20rated%20lower%20if%20they%20were%20for%20use%20only%20in%20adult%20dogs%20or%20did%20not%20specify%20an%20age%20group%20or%20life%20stage%20on%20the%20product%20label.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0We%20read%20customer%20reviews%20to%20determine%20how%20convenient%20it%20was%20to%20use%20the%20shampoos.%20For%20example%2C%20more%20preference%20was%20given%20to%20shampoos%20that%20lathered%20and%20rinsed%20out%20well%20than%20those%20that%20lathered%20poorly.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EScent%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0Shampoos%20with%20light%2C%20long-lasting%20scents%20were%20rated%20more%20highly%20than%20shampoos%20with%20an%20off-putting%20or%20short-lived%20scent.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPurpose%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Shampoos%20that%20delivered%20on%20their%20claims%2C%20according%20to%20customer%20reviews%2C%20were%20rated%20more%20highly%20than%20those%20that%20were%20not%20as%20effective%20as%20promised.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESafety%20for%20puppies%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0Preference%20was%20given%20to%20shampoos%20that%20were%20safe%20for%20puppies%20over%20those%20that%20were%20only%20for%20adult%20dogs%20or%20did%20not%20indicate%20safety%20for%20puppies%20on%20the%20product%20label.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EDog%20shampoo%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3ECan%20I%20use%20human%20shampoo%20on%20a%20dog%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20short%20answer%20is%20no.%20The%20skin%20has%20a%20pH%2C%20which%20indicates%20how%20acidic%20something%20is%3A%20the%20lower%20the%20pH%2C%20the%20more%20acidic.%20The%20pH%20of%20human%20skin%20is%20approximately%205%2C%20while%20canine%20skin%20pH%20is%20slightly%20higher%20(5.5%20to%207.5)%2C%20meaning%20that%20human%20skin%20is%20more%20acidic%20than%20canine%20skin.%20Shampoo%20for%20human%20skin%20is%20too%20acidic%20for%20a%20dog's%20skin%20and%20could%20irritate%20a%20dog's%20eyes.%20%26quot%3BIn%20general%2C%20I%20advise%20pet%20owners%20to%20use%20pet-specific%20shampoos%20whenever%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Todd-Jenkins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20type%20of%20shampoo%20for%20my%20dog%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20depends%20on%20various%20factors%2C%20such%20as%20your%20dog's%20skin%20and%20coat%20health.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20your%20dog%20has%20dry%20and%20itchy%20skin%20from%20environmental%20allergies%2C%20a%20shampoo%20for%20sensitive%20skin%20would%20be%20a%20good%20choice.%20If%20you%20live%20in%20an%20area%20with%20abundant%20fleas%20and%20ticks%2C%20a%20flea%20and%20tick%20shampoo%20could%20accompany%20your%20dog's%20flea%20and%20tick%20preventive.%20Puppies%20need%20specific%20puppy%20shampoo%20that%20is%20formulated%20for%20their%20extra-sensitive%20skin.%20Your%20veterinarian%20can%20help%20you%20determine%20the%20type%20of%20shampoo%20that%20would%20be%20best%20for%20your%20dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20overall%3Cp%3EEarthbath%20Oatmeal%20and%20Aloe%20Pet%20Shampoo%20restores%20moisture%20to%20a%20dog's%20skin%20and%20leaves%20their%20fur%20feeling%20soft.%20It's%20gently%20formulated%20and%20safe%20for%20puppies%20at%20least%206%20weeks%20of%20age%2C%20making%20it%20our%20top%20choice%20for%20the%20best%20dog%20shampoos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shampoo%20is%20especially%20beneficial%20for%20dogs%20with%20sensitive%20skin.%20Dogs%20with%20sensitive%20skin%20need%20a%20hypoallergenic%20shampoo%2C%20free%20of%20ingredients%20that%20could%20irritate%20the%20skin.%20Skin%20conditions%20like%20environmental%20allergies%20to%20dust%20and%20pollen%20can%20make%20a%20dog's%20skin%20itchy%20and%20extra%20sensitive.%20Other%20substances%2C%20such%20as%20synthetic%20fragrances%2C%20can%20also%20irritate%20a%20dog's%20skin%20and%20cause%20persistent%20itchiness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20ingredients%20like%20colloidal%20oatmeal%20and%20aloe%20vera%2C%20the%20shampoo%20relieves%20itchiness%20and%20restores%20the%20skin's%20moisture.%20It%20is%20free%20of%20ingredients%20like%20soap%20and%20synthetic%20fragrances%20that%20could%20cause%20additional%20skin%20irritation%20or%20allergy%20flare-ups.%20Its%20fragrance%20is%20from%20natural%20vanilla%20and%20almond%20oils.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shampoo%20is%20100%25%20biodegradable%2C%20cruelty-free%2C%20and%20will%20not%20wash%20off%20topical%20flea%20and%20tick%20treatments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20fleas%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEditor's%20note%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20shampoo%20from%20Adams%20contains%20pyrethrins.%20Flea%20and%20tick%20shampoos%20that%20contain%20pyrethrins%20and%20permethrin%20are%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%2256f8b61ddb68b43406c40110d566270f%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2220%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.merckvetmanual.com%2Ftoxicology%2Finsecticide-and-acaricide-organic-toxicity%2Fplant-derived-insecticide-toxicosis-in-animals%3Fautoredirectid%3D19576%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etoxic%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20cats%20and%20can%20be%20fatal.%20With%20exposure%2C%20cats%20can%20develop%20symptoms%20such%20as%20tremors%2C%20twitching%2C%20and%20vomiting.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20cat%2C%20choose%20a%20shampoo%20free%20of%20pyrethrins%20and%20permethrin%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_062017_best-dog-shampoo-20%26h%3D0a410dbb8167cae2e60e820ca37864d3179fcc9c720242d6221a5f94defff0b1%26postID%3D61b8efc6f2a36b1ac9f4146a%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-dog-shampoo%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Fsentry-flea-tick-oatmeal-hawaiian%252Fdp%252F56440%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESentry%20Flea%20and%20Tick%20Shampoo%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-flea-treatment-dogs%5C%22%3Ebest%20flea%20treatments%20for%20dogs%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20preventive%20medicines%20like%20spot-ons%2C%20shampoos%20can%20provide%20additional%20protection%20from%20these%20tiny%20pests.%20Adams%20Plus%20Flea%20and%20Tick%20Shampoo%20with%20Precor%20earned%20the%20top%20spot%20in%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-flea-tick-shampoo-dogs%5C%22%3Ebest%20flea%20and%20tick%20shampoo%20for%20dogs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20kills%20flea%20eggs%20and%20larvae%2C%20adult%20fleas%2C%20ticks%2C%20and%20lice%20for%20up%20to%2028%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20shampoo%20contains%20the%20insecticides%20pyrethrins%20and%20S-methoprene.%20Pyrethrins%20are%20synthetic%20insecticides%20commonly%20found%20in%20flea%20and%20tick%20shampoos.%20It%20kills%20insects%20by%20disrupting%20their%20nervous%20system.%20S-methoprene%20is%20an%20insect%20growth%20regulator%20that%20prevents%20flea%20eggs%20from%20reaching%20adulthood.%20Because%20pyrethrins%20are%20highly%20toxic%20to%20cats%2C%20we%20recommend%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_062017_best-dog-shampoo-20%26h%3D0a410dbb8167cae2e60e820ca37864d3179fcc9c720242d6221a5f94defff0b1%26postID%3D61b8efc6f2a36b1ac9f4146a%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-dog-shampoo%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Fsentry-flea-tick-oatmeal-hawaiian%252Fdp%252F56440%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESentry%20Flea%20and%20Tick%20Shampoo%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20households%20with%20felines.%20It%20is%20a%20shorter-acting%20shampoo%20that%20does%20not%20kill%20lice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20formula%20includes%20oatmeal%20to%20soothe%20skin%20that's%20become%20red%20and%20irritated%20from%20scratching.%20It%20is%20safe%20for%20puppies%20at%20least%2012%20weeks%20of%20age.%20The%20shampoo%20should%20be%20left%20on%20for%20at%20least%20five%20minutes%20to%20work%20most%20effectively.%20If%20your%20dog%20has%20a%20heavy%20flea%20infestation%2C%20the%20manufacturer%20recommends%20washing%20your%20pup%20with%20it%20every%20seven%20to%2010%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKeep%20in%20mind%20that%20flea%20and%20tick%20shampoos%20should%20be%20used%20only%20when%20directed%20by%20a%20veterinarian.%20Skin%20conditions%20often%20have%20similar%20symptoms%2C%20like%20redness%20and%20irritation%2C%20and%20what%20looks%20like%20a%20flea%20problem%20might%20be%20something%20else%2C%20such%20as%20a%20yeast%20infection.%20%26quot%3BI%20normally%20discourage%20using%20a%20medicated%20shampoo%20unless%20we%20know%20what%20we're%20treating%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr.%20Karen%20Todd-Jenkins%2C%20a%20relief%20veterinarian%20in%20Trenton%2C%20New%20Jersey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20dry%20shampoo%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20times%20when%20a%20full%20bath%20with%20one%20of%20the%20best%20dog%20shampoos%20isn't%20convenient%20or%20practical.%20Begley's%20Waterless%20Pet%20Shampoo%20is%20an%20easy-to-apply%2C%20lightly%20scented%20shampoo%20that%20cleans%20and%20deodorizes%20without%20drying%20the%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20shampoo%20for%20puppies%20and%20adult%20dogs%20contains%20a%20proprietary%20natural%20enzyme%20blend%20that%20provides%20a%20deep%20clean%20by%20removing%20the%20residues%20of%20protein%2C%20fat%2C%20and%20starch%20from%20a%20dog's%20fur%20and%20skin.%20It%20also%20contains%20naturally%20occurring%20biosurfactants%2C%20which%20are%20produced%20by%20microbes%20and%20boost%20the%20shampoo's%20cleaning%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20available%20in%20four%20natural%2C%20essential%20oil-based%20fragrances%3A%20lavender%2C%20citrus%2C%20oatmeal%20mango%2C%20and%20tea%20tree.%20The%20ingredients%20are%20biodegradable%2C%20making%20it%20a%20safe%20choice%20for%20dogs%20and%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shampoo%20distributes%20quickly%20and%20easily%20across%20a%20dog's%20skin%20and%20coat%20and%20doesn't%20leave%20any%20residue%20after%20it's%20wiped%20off%20with%20a%20towel.%20For%20the%20face%2C%20the%20manufacturer%20recommends%20spraying%20the%20shampoo%20on%20a%20damp%20cloth%20first%20and%20then%20gently%20rubbing%20the%20face%2C%20carefully%20avoiding%20a%20dog's%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWaterless%20shampoos%20are%20often%20helpful%20in%20specific%20situations%2C%20such%20as%20after%20surgery%20when%20a%20dog's%20incision%20site%20has%20to%20stay%20dry%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr.%20Cherese%20Sullivan%2C%20a%20relief%20veterinarian%20in%20Houston%2C%20Texas.%20Dogs%20that%20suffer%20from%20incontinence%20or%20don't%20like%20being%20bathed%20can%20also%20benefit%20from%20the%20quick%20cleaning%20provided%20by%20a%20waterless%20shampoo.%20These%20shampoos%20are%20also%20a%20good%20option%20when%20there's%20a%20long%20time%20between%20grooming%20appointments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBe%20mindful%20that%20waterless%20shampoos%20might%20not%20provide%20the%20same%20level%20of%20cleaning%20that%20a%20bath%20with%20one%20of%20the%20best%20dog%20shampoos%20can%20provide.%20Todd-Jenkins%20says%20that%20bathing%20a%20dog%20with%20water%20and%20shampoo%20does%20a%20superior%20job%20of%20mechanically%20removing%20dirt%20and%20debris%20from%20the%20fur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20puppies%3Cp%3EUnlike%20other%20puppy%20shampoos%20we%20considered%20that%20contained%20synthetic%20ingredients%2C%20Earthbath%20Ultra-Mild%20Puppy%20Shampoo%20uses%20natural%20ingredients%20to%20clean%2C%20condition%2C%20and%20detangle%2C%20making%20it%20our%20top%20choice%20among%20the%20best%20dog%20shampoos%20for%20puppies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20puppy's%20skin%20is%20more%20sensitive%20than%20an%20adult%20dog's%20skin.%20Because%20of%20this%2C%20puppy%20shampoos%20are%20formulated%20to%20be%20extra-gentle%20while%20still%20being%20effective%20at%20cleaning%20and%20moisturizing%20the%20skin%20and%20coat.%20This%20shampoo%20contains%20ingredients%20such%20as%20aloe%20vera%20and%20various%20vitamins%20to%20moisturize%20and%20nourish%20a%20puppy's%20skin%20and%20coat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shampoo%20is%20safe%20for%20puppies%20at%20least%206%20weeks%20of%20age%20and%20does%20not%20wash%20off%20topical%20flea%20and%20tick%20treatments.%20For%20the%20first%20few%20weeks%20of%20life%2C%20puppies%20have%20trouble%20regulating%20their%20body%20temperature%2C%20so%20they%20can%20get%20cold%20easily.%20Because%20of%20this%2C%20it%20is%20recommended%20that%20puppies%20not%20be%20bathed%20until%20they%20are%20at%20least%206%20to%208%20weeks%20old%20when%20they're%20better%20at%20regulating%20their%20body%20temperature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarthbath%20Ultra-Mild%20Puppy%20Shampoo%20lathers%20well%20and%20rinses%20easily%2C%20which%20helps%20if%20you%20have%20a%20squirmy%20puppy%20that%20doesn't%20like%20to%20hold%20still%20for%20a%20long%20bath.%20The%20gentle%2C%20tear-free%20formula%20will%20not%20sting%20a%20puppy's%20eyes%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20take%20extra%20care%20to%20avoid%20the%20eyes%2C%20nose%2C%20and%20mouth%20when%20bathing%20a%20dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20whitening%3Cp%3EDogs%20with%20white%20fur%20need%20more%20than%20just%20regular%20shampoo.%20They%20need%20a%20shampoo%20that%20also%20removes%20discoloring%20stains%2C%20like%20urine%20and%20food%2C%20that%20are%20more%20obvious%20on%20white%20coats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChris%20Christensen%20White%20on%20White%20Shampoo%20for%20Pets%20whitens%20and%20brightens%20a%20dog's%20fur%20for%20four%20weeks%20without%20relying%20on%20harsh%20chemicals%20like%20bleaching%20agents.%20It%20also%20removes%20yellow%20stains%20and%20provides%20a%20deep%20clean.%20As%20a%20bonus%2C%20the%20shampoo%20can%20be%20used%20on%20dogs%20with%20any%20coat%20color%20to%20increase%20the%20fur's%20luster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhitening%20shampoos%20are%20primarily%20classified%20as%20bluing%2C%20enzymatic%2C%20or%20clarifying.%20Bluing%20shampoos%2C%20also%20called%20optical%20brighteners%2C%20contain%20blue%20or%20purple%20color%20enhancers%20that%20absorb%20and%20reflect%20light%20to%20hide%20stains.%20Enzymatic%20shampoos%20break%20down%20proteins%20that%20cause%20discoloration.%20Clarifying%20shampoos%20strip%20dirt%20from%20the%20hair%20cuticles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20shampoo%20has%20a%20purple%20color%20that%20provides%20an%20optical%20brightening%20effect.%20It%20should%20be%20left%20on%20for%20up%20to%2010%20minutes%3B%20if%20left%20on%20longer%2C%20it%20may%20leave%20a%20slight%20purple%20tint%20on%20the%20fur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20shampoo's%20formula%20is%20gentle%2C%20the%20manufacturer%20recommends%20testing%20the%20shampoo%20in%20a%20small%20skin%20area%20if%20a%20dog%20has%20allergies.%20It%20is%20safe%20for%20puppies%20at%20least%2016%20weeks%20of%20age%20and%20adult%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20dog%20shampoo%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20shopping%20for%20a%20dog%20shampoo%2C%20there%20are%20several%20things%20to%20keep%20in%20mind.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIngredients%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Look%20for%20shampoos%20that%20contain%20100%25%2C%20or%20nearly%20100%25%2C%20natural%20ingredients.%20These%20ingredients%20are%20less%20likely%20to%20cause%20irritation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAge%20and%20safety%20for%20puppies%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Make%20sure%20the%20shampoo%20you%20use%20is%20labeled%20for%20your%20dog's%20age.%20If%20a%20recommended%20age%20isn't%20clearly%20stated%20on%20the%20label%2C%20we%20recommend%20contacting%20the%20manufacturer%20for%20the%20information.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EScent%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Natural%2C%20light%20fragrances%20are%20best.%20This%20ensures%20both%20you%20and%20your%20dog%20aren't%20put%20off%20by%20powerful%20scents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPurpose%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EShampoos%20are%20formulated%20for%20specific%20needs.%20A%20simple%20cleansing%20and%20moisturizing%20shampoo%2C%20like%20our%20top%20pick%2C%20is%20suitable%20for%20most%20dogs.%20But%20if%20you're%20looking%20to%20prevent%20and%20treat%20fleas%2C%20brighten%20your%20dog's%20white%20coat%2C%20or%20treat%20a%20particular%20skin%20condition%2C%20the%20shampoo%20should%20be%20labeled%20for%20that%20use.%20If%20your%20dog%20has%20a%20skin%20condition%2C%20it's%20best%20to%20check%20with%20your%20veterinarian%20before%20choosing%20a%20shampoo%3B%20for%20certain%20conditions%2C%20they%20may%20recommend%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-medicated-shampoo-for-dogs%5C%22%3Ebest%20medicated%20shampoos%20for%20dogs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20selected%20the%20best%20dog%20shampoos%3Cp%3EWe%20consulted%20with%20two%20veterinarians%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20dog%20shampoos.%20While%20they%20didn't%20provide%20specific%20recommendations%2C%20they%20shared%20their%20clinical%20expertise%20regarding%20how%20dog%20shampoos%20can%20be%20used%20for%20different%20purposes.%20We%20also%20researched%20how%20dog%20shampoos%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20selection%20criteria%20that%20we%20used%20to%20evaluate%20the%20best%20dog%20shampoos%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIngredients%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20analyzed%20the%20ingredients%20list%20of%20each%20shampoo%20to%20identify%20natural%20and%20synthetic%20ingredients.%20Preference%20was%20given%20to%20shampoos%20that%20contained%20natural%20ingredients%20that%20are%20gentle%20on%20a%20dog's%20skin.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAge%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0Except%20for%20puppy%20shampoos%2C%20shampoos%20were%20rated%20higher%20if%20they%20were%20safe%20for%20puppies%20and%20adult%20dogs.%20They%20were%20rated%20lower%20if%20they%20were%20for%20use%20only%20in%20adult%20dogs%20or%20did%20not%20specify%20an%20age%20group%20or%20life%20stage%20on%20the%20product%20label.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0We%20read%20customer%20reviews%20to%20determine%20how%20convenient%20it%20was%20to%20use%20the%20shampoos.%20For%20example%2C%20more%20preference%20was%20given%20to%20shampoos%20that%20lathered%20and%20rinsed%20out%20well%20than%20those%20that%20lathered%20poorly.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EScent%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0Shampoos%20with%20light%2C%20long-lasting%20scents%20were%20rated%20more%20highly%20than%20shampoos%20with%20an%20off-putting%20or%20short-lived%20scent.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPurpose%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Shampoos%20that%20delivered%20on%20their%20claims%2C%20according%20to%20customer%20reviews%2C%20were%20rated%20more%20highly%20than%20those%20that%20were%20not%20as%20effective%20as%20promised.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESafety%20for%20puppies%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0Preference%20was%20given%20to%20shampoos%20that%20were%20safe%20for%20puppies%20over%20those%20that%20were%20only%20for%20adult%20dogs%20or%20did%20not%20indicate%20safety%20for%20puppies%20on%20the%20product%20label.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDog%20shampoo%20FAQs%3Ch3%3ECan%20I%20use%20human%20shampoo%20on%20a%20dog%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20short%20answer%20is%20no.%20The%20skin%20has%20a%20pH%2C%20which%20indicates%20how%20acidic%20something%20is%3A%20the%20lower%20the%20pH%2C%20the%20more%20acidic.%20The%20pH%20of%20human%20skin%20is%20approximately%205%2C%20while%20canine%20skin%20pH%20is%20slightly%20higher%20(5.5%20to%207.5)%2C%20meaning%20that%20human%20skin%20is%20more%20acidic%20than%20canine%20skin.%20Shampoo%20for%20human%20skin%20is%20too%20acidic%20for%20a%20dog's%20skin%20and%20could%20irritate%20a%20dog's%20eyes.%20%26quot%3BIn%20general%2C%20I%20advise%20pet%20owners%20to%20use%20pet-specific%20shampoos%20whenever%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Todd-Jenkins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20type%20of%20shampoo%20for%20my%20dog%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20depends%20on%20various%20factors%2C%20such%20as%20your%20dog's%20skin%20and%20coat%20health.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20your%20dog%20has%20dry%20and%20itchy%20skin%20from%20environmental%20allergies%2C%20a%20shampoo%20for%20sensitive%20skin%20would%20be%20a%20good%20choice.%20If%20you%20live%20in%20an%20area%20with%20abundant%20fleas%20and%20ticks%2C%20a%20flea%20and%20tick%20shampoo%20could%20accompany%20your%20dog's%20flea%20and%20tick%20preventive.%20Puppies%20need%20specific%20puppy%20shampoo%20that%20is%20formulated%20for%20their%20extra-sensitive%20skin.%20Your%20veterinarian%20can%20help%20you%20determine%20the%20type%20of%20shampoo%20that%20would%20be%20best%20for%20your%20dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-shampoo%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711744048000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66071cf01caec1275a6b0b32%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-shampoo%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20best%20dog%20shampoos%20clean%20and%20moisturize%20skin%20and%20coat.%20Our%20top%20veteri