ce%20Department%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Handy%20kissed%20and%20touched%20a%209-year-old%20girl%20in%20Glendale%2C%20California.%20The%20police%20investigation%20also%20revealed%20that%20there%20were%20more%20children%20in%20LA%2C%20Michigan%2C%20and%20North%20Carolina%20that%20Handy%20preyed%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20%26quot%3BQuiet%20on%20Set%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20searched%20Handy's%20home%20and%20uncovered%20disturbing%20journal%20entries%20in%20which%20he%20described%20himself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bfull-blown%26quot%3B%20pedophile.%20They%20found%20over%2010%2C000%20images%20of%20child%20pornography%2C%20including%201%2C768%20images%20of%20young%20girls%20in%20erotic%20poses%2C%20238%20images%20of%20young%20girls%20in%20sexually%20explicit%20poses%2C%20and%20two%20images%20of%20girls%20engaged%20in%20bondage%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20also%20video%20files%20of%20minors%20engaged%20in%20sexually%20explicit%20conduct%20and%20Ziploc%20bags%20with%20girls'%20names%20on%20them%2C%20containing%20%26quot%3Btokens.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20contacted%20MJ%20after%20seeing%20a%20bag%20with%20Brandi's%20name%20on%20it%2C%20filled%20with%20letters%20that%20she%20had%20written.%20Other%20bags%20contained%20the%20underwear%20of%20other%20girls%2C%20including%20a%207-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMJ%20said%20that%20many%20parents%20of%20the%20children%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20investigation%2C%20but%20she%20agreed%20to%20let%20Brandi%20talk%20to%20the%20detectives%20in%20the%20hopes%20that%20they%20could%20serve%20justice%20and%20get%20closure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHandy%20pleaded%20no%20contest%20in%202004%20and%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Farchives%2Fla-xpm-2012-jan-08-la-fi-ct-hollywood-molesters-20120109-story.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esentenced%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20six%20years%20in%20prison%20on%20two%20felony%20counts%2C%20for%20lewd%20acts%20with%20a%20child%20under%2014%20and%20for%20distributing%20sexually%20explicit%20material%2C%20and%20one%20misdemeanor%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBrandi%20quit%20the%20entertainment%20industry%20after%20her%20experience%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22MJ%20in%20episode%20two%20of%20the%20docuseries%20%26quot%3BQuiet%20on%20Set.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66070faa1caec1275a6b02b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMJ%20in%20episode%20two%20of%20the%20docuseries%20%26quot%3BQuiet%20on%20Set.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EInvestigation%20Discovery%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20left%20the%20business%20and%20never%20returned%2C%26quot%3B%20MJ%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20no%20longer%20trusted%20anybody%20with%20children%20in%20this%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20abandoned.%20There%20was%20never%20any%20apology%20to%20Brandi%20herself%20for%20what%20happened.%20Everything%20got%20swept%20under%20the%20rug.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrandi's%20current%20whereabouts%20are%20unknown%2C%20but%20people%20on%20TikTok%20have%20been%20theorizing%20about%20what%20happened%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20theory%20is%20that%20she's%2010-time%20Grammy%20winner%20Brandi%20Carlile%2C%20which%20doesn't%20make%20sense%20because%20the%20singer%20doesn't%20have%20a%20history%20of%20appearing%20on%20Nickelodeon%20as%20a%20kid%20and%20her%20age%20doesn't%20align%20with%20Brandi's%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40pamelawurstvetrini%2Fvideo%2F7349939717263117611%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etheory%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20that%20Business%20Insider%20reporter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fkate-taylor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKate%20Taylor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20appeared%20in%20%26quot%3BQuiet%20on%20Set%26