0Maalouf%20posted%20online.%20The%20clip%20showed%20the%20YouTuber%20at%20a%20hotel%20in%20Haiti.%20In%20the%20video%2C%20he%20said%20that%20he%20and%20his%20crew%20intended%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20capital%20city%20of%20Port-au-Prince%2C%20but%20had%20to%20wait%20until%20the%20early%20morning%20hours%20so%20they%20could%20arrive%20in%20the%20sunlight.%20He%20also%20noted%20that%20Port-au-Prince%20is%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20run%20by%20gangs%26quot%3B%20and%20even%20though%20they%20had%20secured%20safe%20passage%2C%20%26quot%3Ball%20it%20takes%20is%20one%20stupid%20gang%20member%20holding%20an%20AK-47%20for%20one%20thing%20to%20go%20wrong%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20the%20last%20video%20he%20recorded%20before%20he%20got%20kidnapped%2C%20if%20you%20have%20his%20number%20pls%20don't%20text%20him%20while%20he's%20in%20there%20for%20safety%20reasons.%20%F0%9F%99%8F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FJJ7y1uVjGA%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FJJ7y1uVjGA%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Lalem%20(%40Lalem)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLalem%2Fstatus%2F1773539719567065119%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2029%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2010%2C%20Mr%20Maalouf%20also%20posted%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20on%20another%20one%20of%20those%20trips%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20die%2C%20thanks%20for%20watching%20what%20I've%20put%20out.%20If%20I%20live%2C%20all%20glory%20to%20God%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FYourFellowArab%2Fstatus%2F1767014442779525154%5C%22%3EX%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20Friday%2C%20another%20YouTuber%2C%20Miles%20%26quot%3BLord%20Miles%26quot%3B%20Routledge%2C%20claimed%20that%20he%20spoke%20to%20the%20kidnapped%20streamer.%20In%20a%20series%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Freal_lord_miles%2Fstatus%2F1773586219529564511%5C%22%3Etweets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mr%20Routledge%20said%20that%20Mr%20Maalouf%20was%20travelling%20with%20a%20fixer%20called%20Sean%20Roubens%20Jean%20Sacra%2C%20who%20was%20also%20kidnapped.%20%26quot%3BArab%20has%20been%20kept%20in%20a%20cage%20in%20a%20place%20on%20the%20eastern%20outskirts%20of%20the%20Capital%2C%20Port-au-Prince%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArab%20has%20stated%20that%20despite%20the%20hardships%2C%20he's%20going%20to%20come%20out%20with%20a%20great%20video%20after%20this%2C%20and%20he%20should%20be%20out%20in%20no%20time.%20Sean%20was%20actually%20offered%20to%20be%20let%20go%2C%20but%20he's%20a%20great%20guy%20and%20doesn't%20want%20to%20leave%20Arab%20on%20his%20own%2C%20so%20he%20has%20decided%20to%20stay%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Routledge%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fafter-sneakers-and-nfts-donald-trump-is-selling-god-bless-the-usa-bibles-for-60-5333947%5C%22%3EAfter%20Sneakers%20And%20NFTs%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20Is%20Selling%20%26quot%3BGod%20Bless%20The%20USA%26quot%3B%20Bibles%20For%20%2460%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Routledge%20also%20criticised%20the%20US%20government%20and%20the%20State%20Department%20for%20failing%20to%20secure%20Mr%20Maalouf's%20release.%20He%20said%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bvery%20hands-off%20on%20helping%2C%20even%20though%20Arab%20is%20a%20US%20citizen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20The%20State%20Department%20confirmed%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Baware%20of%20reports%20of%20the%20kidnapping%20of%20a%20US%20citizen%20in%20Haiti%26quot%3B%20but%20would%20not%20provide%20any%20details.%20%26quot%3BThe%20US%20Department%20of%20State%20and%20our%20embassies%20and%20consulates%20abroad%20have%20no%20higher%20priority%20than%20the%20safety%20and%20security%