C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbyju-s-secures-50-vote-on-rights-issue-offers-investors-chance-to-invest-124032900383_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbyju-s-secures-50-vote-on-rights-issue-offers-investors-chance-to-invest-124032900383_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbyju-s-secures-50-vote-on-rights-issue-offers-investors-chance-to-invest-124032900383_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20hot%20new%20government%20job%20is%20AI%20specialist%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20robotic%20hand%20using%20laptop%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6606ff0b3f923f7dab02bc46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20White%20House%20wants%20federal%20agencies%20to%20hire%20up%20AI%20officers%20if%20they're%20going%20to%20use%20the%20tech.%3Cp%3EKilito%20Chan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Biden%20Administration%20is%20beefing%20up%20AI%20staff%20across%20the%20government.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAll%20federal%20agencies%20are%20now%20required%20to%20hire%20a%20chief%20AI%20specialist%2C%20Kamala%20Harris%20announced.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAgencies%20must%20prove%20their%20AI%20tools%20don't%20harm%20the%20public%2C%20or%20stop%20using%20AI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWant%20to%20work%20for%20the%20federal%20government%3F%20Consider%20becoming%20an%20AI%20specialist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20administration%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fstatements-releases%2F2024%2F03%2F28%2Ffact-sheet-vice-president-harris-announces-omb-policy-to-advance-governance-innovation-and-risk-management-in-federal-agencies-use-of-artificial-intelligence%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%20that%20it%20will%20be%20beefing%20up%20AI%20staff%20across%20all%20federal%20agencies%2C%20aiming%20to%20hire%20100%20AI%20professionals%20by%20the%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20all%20federal%20agencies%20must%20hire%20a%20chief%20AI%20specialist%20to%20oversee%20the%20ethical%20and%20transparent%20use%20of%20AI%2C%20the%20White%20House's%20Office%20of%20Management%20and%20Budget%20(OMB)%20said%20in%20its%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20AI%20is%20used%20responsibly%2C%20understanding%20that%20we%20must%20have%20senior%20leaders%20across%20our%20government%20who%20are%20specifically%20tasked%20with%20overseeing%20AI%20adoption%20and%20use%2C%26quot%3B%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20said%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fspeeches-remarks%2F2024%2F03%2F28%2Fpress-call-by-vice-president-harris-on-artificial-intelligence%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DFirst%252C%2520we%2520are%2520announcing%2520new%2Csafety%2520of%2520the%2520American%2520people.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20press%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20hiring%20AI%20officers%2C%20the%20agencies%20must%20also%20set%20up%20AI%20Governance%20Boards%2C%20like%20those%20that%20already%20exist%20at%20the%20Departments%20of%20Defense%2C%20Veterans%20Affairs%2C%20Housing%20and%20Urban%20Development%2C%20and%20State%20Department%2C%20according%20to%20the%20OMB.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20AI%20roles%20offer%20employees%20some%20major%20perks%2C%20including%20incentives%20of%20up%20to%2025%25%20of%20their%20basic%20pay%20(plus%20extra%20multiplied%20by%20the%20years%20in%20the%20service%20agreement)%20for%20relocation%2C%20recruitment%2C%20and%20retention%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chcoc.gov%2Fcontent%2Fpay-flexibility-incentive-pay-and-leave-and-workforce-flexibility-programs-artificial%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ememo%20from%20the%20US%20Office%20of%20Personnel%20Management%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20office%20also%20encourages%20agencies%20to%20offer%20flexible%20work%20schedules%20and%20remote%20work%20options%20to%20those%20filling%20critical%20AI%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpen%20positions%20listed%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fai.usajobs.gov%2Fsearch%2Fresults%2F%3Fcmco%3DAI%26s%3Dsalary%26sd%3Ddesc%26p%3D1%26k%3D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20government%20job%20board%3C%2Fa%3E%20show%20base%20salaries%20topping%20out%20at%20over%20%24143%2C000%20for%20certain%20IT%20specialists%20dealing%20with%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20order%2C%20agencies%20must%20also%20prove%20that%20their%20use%20of%20AI%20does%20not%20hurt%20the%20public%2C%20and%20if%20they%20can't%2C%20they%20must%20immediately%20stop%20using%20AI%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarris%20explained%20that%2C%20for%20example%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Veterans%20Administration%20wants%20to%20use%20AI%20in%20VA%20hospitals%20to%20help%20doctors%20diagnose%20patients%2C%20they%20would%20first%20have%20to%20demonstrate%20that%20AI%20does%20not%20produce%20racially%20biased%20diagnoses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20policy%20also%20sets%20up%20a%20number%20of%20guidelines%20that%20federal%20agencies%20must%20adopt%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20including%20publishing%20an%20annual%20inventory%20of%20their%20use%20of%20AI%2C%20releasing%20any%20government-owned%20AI%20code%20they%20use%2C%20and%20making%20sure%20a%20human%20oversees%20all%20AI%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20expansion%20of%20the%20government's%20AI%20workforce%20is%20the%20latest%20part%20of%20Biden's%20AI%20plan%2C%20which%20kicked%20off%20with%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fpresidential-actions%2F2023%2F10%2F30%2Fexecutive-order-on-the-safe-secure-and-trustworthy-development-and-use-of-artificial-intelligence%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexecutive%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20October%20setting%20up%20transparency%20policies%20around%20the%20buzzy%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgovernment-jobs-hiring-ai-specialists-white-house-biden-harris-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711735008000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6607001d1caec1275a6afa93%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgovernment-jobs-hiring-ai-specialists-white-house-biden-harris-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20White%20house%20announced%20this%20week%20it%20will%20require%20all%20federal%20agencies%20to%20hire%20a%20chief%20AI%20officer%20and%20set%20up%20an%20AI%20Governance%20Board.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ggoodwin%40businessinsider.com%20(Grace%20Eliza%20Goodwin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgovernment-jobs-hiring-ai-specialists-white-house-biden-harris-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Priyanka%2C%20Nick%20attend%20Mannara's%20birthday%20bash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711734855000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108883963%2Cimgsize-77614.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fpriyanka-chopra-nick-jonas-madhu-chopra-attend-mannara-chopras-33rd-birthday-bash-in-mumbai%2Farticleshow%2F108883964.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108883964.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EMannara%20Chopra%2C%20who%20recently%20rose%20to%20fame%20with%20her%20stint%20in%20Bigg%20Boss%2017%2C%20has%20turned%2033%20today%20(March%2029)%20and%20she