akistan-aseefa-bhutto-zardari-elected-unopposed-as-member-of-national-assembly%2Farticleshow%2F108884023.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-aseefa-bhutto-zardari-elected-unopposed-as-member-of-national-assembly%2Famp_articleshow%2F108884023.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-aseefa-bhutto-zardari-elected-unopposed-as-member-of-national-assembly%2Famp_articleshow%2F108884023.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Battleground%3A%20Modi%20Factor%20vs%20Congress%20Guarantees%20-%20What%20Karnataka%20Wants%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20its%2028%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20huge%20contribution%20to%20the%20country's%20GDP%20and%20as%20the%20home%20of%20the%20IT%20capital%20of%20India%2C%20success%20in%20Karnataka%20would%20be%20high%20on%20every%20party's%20wishlist%20for%20the%20upcoming%20elections%20based%20on%20these%20factors%20alone.%20But%20what%20makes%20the%20state%20even%20more%20important%20is%20because%20the%20BJP%20sees%20it%20as%20the%20gateway%20to%20South%20India%20and%20is%20hoping%20to%20make%20inroads%20into%20the%20region%20based%20on%20its%20consistently%20good%20performances%20in%20Karnataka%20while%20the%20Congress%20is%20looking%20to%20push%20the%20party%20out%20by%20eating%20into%20its%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20itself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20NDTV's%20special%20show%20'Battleground'%20on%20Friday%2C%20a%20panel%20of%20experts%20discussed%20the%20key%20issues%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Karnataka%20and%20its%20capital%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20whether%20the%20Modi%20Factor%20will%20play%20a%20bigger%20role%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20or%20Congress'%20guarantees%2C%20which%20contributed%20to%20the%20party%20sweeping%20the%20state%20in%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20won%2025%20constituencies%20in%20Karnataka%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20has%20got%20the%20most%20number%20of%20seats%20of%20any%20party%20in%20the%20state%20every%20time%20since%20the%202004%20general%20elections.%20Another%20interesting%20statistic%2C%20revealed%20by%20CSDS%20surveys%2C%20is%20that%20while%20one%20in%20three%20voters%20who%20cast%20their%20ballots%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20other%20states%20in%202014%20and%202019%20said%20they%20had%20done%20so%20because%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20the%20proportion%20for%20Karnataka%20was%20nearly%2055%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPsephologist%20and%20educationist%20Sandeep%20Shastri%20-%20one%20of%20the%20panellists%20on%20the%20show%20anchored%20by%20NDTV%20Editor-in-Chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia%20-%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOf%20the%20130%20seats%20in%20the%20South%2C%20the%20NDA%20won%2030%20in%202019...%20Voters%20in%20Karnataka%20cast%20their%20ballots%20differently%20in%20the%20Assembly%20and%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections...%20At%20one%20level%2C%20the%20Modi%20factor%20is%20the%20key%20to%20the%20BJP's%20campaign.%20What%20they%20are%20doing%20is%20bringing%20caste%20and%20class%20together.%20Much%20of%20their%20politics%20is%20caste-based%2C%20but%20class%20inclusive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shastri%20said%20the%20BJP's%20candidates%20will%20appeal%20to%20people%20and%20say%20they%20are%20not%20voting%20for%20individuals%20but%20actually%20giving%20another%20seat%20to%20PM%20Modi.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20said%2C%20the%20party%20will%20also%20focus%20on%20caste%20and%20class%20at%20the%20local%20level.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20focusing%20on%20local%20issues.%20So%20this%20election%20will%20be%20a%20contest%20between%20the%20national%20narrative%20and%20the%20local%20narrative%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20journalist%20and%20author%20Sugata%20Srinivasaraju%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20looking%20at%20the%202024%20election%2C%20especially%20the%20south%2C%20from%20the%20point%20of%20view%20of%20whether%20the%20BJP%20is%20going%20to%20go%20beyond%20Karnataka%20and%20make%20an%20imprint%20in%20other%20states...%20and%20also%20the%20Congress%20has%20pegged%20a%20lot%20of%20hope%20on%20the%20south.%20So%2C%20for%20these%20two%20factors%2C%20the%20south%20is%20going%20to%20be%20important%20for%20both%20parties.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20time%20the%20Congress%20(in%20Karnataka)%20is%20in%20a%20reasonably%20better%20position.%20Last%20time%20they%20had%20one%20seat%2C%20so%20obviously%20they%20will%20do%20better%20than%20one%20seat...%20The%20narrative%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20trying%20to%20build%20on%20unemployment%20may%20become%20very%20important%20in%20this%20election...%20But%20the%20Congress%20does%20not%20have%20a%20cultural%20narrative%20and%20makes%20a%20technocratic%20argument%2C%20and%20that%20may%20not%20work%20in%20a%20general%20election%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Congress'%20guarantees%2C%20which%20helped%20the%20party%20win%20135%20of%20the%20state's%20234%20seats%20in%20the%202023%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20TV%20Mohandas%20Pai%2C%20Chairman%2C%20Aarin%20Capital%20Partners%2C%20said%20people%20will%20probably%20give%20PM%20Modi's%20guarantee%20a%20chance%20this%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOut%20of%2096%20crore%20voters%2C%2055%20crore%20are%20below%20the%20age%20of%2040%2C%20so%20how%20they%20vote%20this%20time%20will%20be%20important.%20In%20Karnataka%2C%20people%20have%20got%20all%20the%20guarantees%20from%20(Chief%20Minister)%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20the%20Congress.%20The%20state%20has%20no%20more%20money.%20Now%20they%20want%20Modi's%20guarantee%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20want%20PM%20Modi's%20development.%20He%20has%20made%20sure%20almost%20every%20Indian%20has%20a%20bank%20account%2C%20food%20on%20the%20table%2C%20a%20roof%20over%20their%20head%20and%20health%20insurance%2C%20et%20cetera.%20Deprivation%20is%20less.%20And%20this%20can%20be%20seen%2C%20it%20is%20there%20on%20the%20ground%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Focus%20On%20Entrepreneurship'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20panellist%2C%20Nooraine%20Fazal%2C%20Founding%20Managing%20Trustee%20And%20CEO%20of%20Inventure%20Academy%2C%20said%20India%20was%20aspirational%20even%20when%20her%20generation%20was%20growing%20up%2C%20but%20it%20lacked%20the%20confidence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20no%20matter%20where%20you%20go%20in%20the%20world%20as%20an%20Indian%2C%20you%20can%20go%20with%20your%20head%20held%20high.%20When%20I%20first%20went%20out%20as%20a%20student%2C%20people%20would%20ask%20'do%20you%20have%20tigers%20where%20you%20live%2C%20how%20is%20your%20English%20so%20good%3F'%20Now%2C%20that%20has%20changed%20thanks%20to%20Bengaluru.%20People%20now%20ask%20'do%20you%20work%20in%20IT%2C%20do%20you%20come%20from%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%20of%20India%3F'%26quot%3B%20she%20pointed%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Fazal%20said%20her%20focus%20in%20the%20elections%20will%20be%20on%20which%20party%20is%20looking%20at%20fixing%20the%20educational%20system%20and%20harnessing%20India's%20potential.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20embrace%20policies%20such%20as%20the%20new%20educational%20policy...%20We%20need%20to%20focus%20on%20employability%2C%20entrepreneurship%20and%20enhancing%20ease%20of%20doing%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYourStory%20Founder%20Shradha%20Sharma%20said%20she%20is%20from%20Bihar%20and%20Bengaluru%20had%20welcomed%20her%20with%20open%20arms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20people%20know%20everything.%20Young%20India%20and%20women%20know%20everything.%20India%20is%20no%20longer%20apologetic.%20Young%20India%20is%20looking%20at%20the%20next%2010%20years.%20When%20you%20see%20startups%20like%20Ola%2C%20Zerodha%2C%20Flipkart%20and%20others%2C%20they%20are%20proud%20that%20they%20are%20creating%20employment.%20Their%20focus%20is%20on%20understanding%20which%20government%20will%20ensure%20that%20the%20next%2010%20years%20will%20be%20India's%20decade%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711734420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fa07k4k28_karnataka-battleground_625x300_29_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-battleground-modi-factor-vs-congress-guarantees-what-karnataka-wants-5335804%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20its%2028%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20huge%20contribution%20to%20the%20country's%20GDP%20and%20as%20the%20home%20of%20the%20IT%20capital%20of%20India%2C%20success%20in%20Karnataka%20would%20be%20high%20on%20every%20party's%20wishlist%20for%20the%20upcoming%20elections%20based%20on%20these%20factors%20alone.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-battleground-modi-factor-vs-congress-guarantees-what-karnataka-wants-5335804%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-battleground-modi-factor-vs-congress-guarantees-what-karnataka-wants-5335804%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-battleground-modi-factor-vs-congress-guarantees-what-karnataka-wants-5335804%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Retired%20Railway%20Employee%20Who%20Took%20On%20Gangster-Politician%20Mukhtar%20Ansari%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20stealing%20of%202%2C000%20bricks%20was%20the%20first%20trigger.%20The%20second%20was%20the%20land%20grab.%20Both%20allegedly%20by%20gangster-politician%20Mukhtar%20Ansari's%20men.%20He%20had%20retired%20in%202003%20but%20there%20was%20no%20rest%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarish%20Chandra%20Vishwakarma%2C%20a%20former%20railway%20employee%2C%20filed%20a%20land-grab%20case%20against%20regional%20strongman%20Mukhtar%20Ansari%20the%20same%20year.%20It%20became%20the%20first%20land-grab%20case%20in%20a%20long%20list%20of%20cases%20against%20the%20regional%20heavyweight%2C%20who%20died%20of%20a%20cardiac%20arrest%20at%20a%20hospital%20in%20Banda%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20on%20Thursday.%20He%20was%2063.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20have%20to%20die%20one%20day.%20It%20is%20both%20your%20story%20and%20mine%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Vishwakarma%2C%2082%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Mau%2C%20told%20NDTV%20philosophically%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20gangster's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202005%2C%20till%20his%20death%2C%20Mukhtar%20Ansari%20had%20been%20lodged%20in%20different%20jails%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Punjab.%20The%20gangster%20won%20the%20Mau%20assembly%20seat%20five%20times%20in%20a%20row%2C%20including%20twice%20as%20a%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20land%20opposite%20my%20house%20which%20was%20allegedly%20taken%20over%20by%20Mukhtar%20Ansari's%20men.%20A%20school%20was%20built%20there%20and%20Mukhtar%20Ansari%20was%20called%20to%20inaugurate%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Vishwakarma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20build%20a%20road%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20school%2C%20his%20(Mukhtar%20Ansari)%20men%20stole%20the%202%2C000%20bricks%20that%20I%20had%20bought%20to%20build%20my%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mukhtar%20Ansari%20-%20who%20hailed%20from%20Mau%20and%20was%20believed%20to%20have%20strong%20influence%20in%20Ghazipur%20and%20Varanasi%20districts%20as%20well%20-%20came%20to%20inaugurate%20the%20school%2C%20he%20was%20weighed%20in%20coins%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20inquiring%2C%20the%20retired%20railway%20employee%20found%20that%20the%20land%20belonged%20to%20the%20state%20government.%20He%20promptly%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20Mukhtar%20Ansari%20and%20his%20men.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20how%20he%20managed%20the%20money%2C%20Mr%20Vishwakarma%20said%20he%20used%20his%20pension%20to%20fight%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vishwakarma%20says%20his%20big%20brother%20was%20assaulted%20by%20Mukhtar%20Ansari's%20men%20as%20he%20refused%20to%20withdraw%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20won%20after%20many%20years%2C%20the%20school%20was%20closed%20and%20the%20Mau%20Nagarapalika%20took%20over%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20never%20found%20the%20stolen%20bricks%2C%20but%20Mr%20Vishwakarma%2C%20who%20lost%20his%20wife%20in%202018%2C%20was%20able%20to%20build%20his%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711734420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fr77gi18_mau-resident-1200-_625x300_29_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-retired-railway-employee-who-took-on-gangster-politician-mukhtar-ansari-5335404%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20stealing%20of%202%2C000%20bricks%20was%20the%20first%20trigger.%20The%20second%20was%20the%20land%20grab.%20Both%20allegedly%20by%20gangster-politician%20Mukhtar%20Ansari's%20men.%20He%20had%20retired%20in%202003%20but%20there%20was%20no%20rest%20period.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-retired-railway-employee-who-took-on-gangster-politician-mukhtar-ansari-5335404%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Munna%20Tripathi%20will%20return%20in%20Mirzapur%203'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711733716000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108883859%2Cimgsize-33686.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmirzapur-3-ritesh-sidhwani-reveals-divyenndu-will-come-back-as-munna-tripathi-but-in-an-unexpected-manner%2Farticleshow%2F108883862.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%2