20after%20her%20throat%20closed%20up%20when%20given%20a%20shot%20of%20lip%20dissolver%20by%20her%20aesthetician.%20She%20was%20left%20%26quot%3Bgasping%20for%20air%26quot%3B%20while%20her%20face%20ballooned%20to%20double%20its%20size%20minutes%20after%20being%20given%20the%20shot%20in%20January.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2024-year-old%20had%20lip%20filler%20injected%20twice%20before%20to%20plump%20up%20her%20pout.%20She%20got%20her%20first%200.5ml%20of%20lip%20filler%20when%20she%20was%2018%2C%20and%20an%20additional%201ml%20at%2022.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20dissolve%20her%20existing%20filler%20before%20topping%20up%20with%20another%201ml.%20However%2C%20the%2024-year-old%20experienced%20a%20severe%20allergic%20reaction%20moments%20after%20the%20dissolver%20was%20injected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20went%20to%20have%20my%20lip%20filler%20dissolved%20and%20I%20didn't%20think%20anything%20of%20it%20because%20I'd%20had%20lip%20filler%20put%20in%20in%20the%20past%20and%20it%20was%20all%20fine%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Harris%20said%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2024%2F03%2F26%2Fwomans-face-ballooned-twice-size-getting-lip-filler-dissolved-20532910%2F%3Fico%3Dread_more_related_video_carousel%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMetro%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Harris%20revealed%20that%20the%20complications%20began%20when%20the%201ml%20she%20wanted%20to%20dissolve%20had%20%26quot%3Bmigrated%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BStraight%20away%20I%20knew%20something%20wasn't%20right.%20She%20gave%20me%20the%20dissolver%20and%20my%20lips%20just%20blew%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20asked%20the%20aesthetician%20if%20it%20was%20normal%20and%20she%20said%20'yeah%20people's%20lips%20do%20tend%20to%20swell%20up'%20but%20it%20didn't%20look%20normal%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20recalled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2024-year-old%20further%20said%20that%20she%20started%20to%20get%20itchy%20and%20painful%20hives%20all%20over%20her%20eyelids%20in%20the%20next%20five%20minutes.%20%26quot%3BThen%20within%2010%20minutes%2C%20my%20face%20was%20all%20blown%20up%20and%20swollen.%20I%20couldn't%20see%20out%20of%20my%20eyes%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20looked%20unrecognisable%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Felon-musk-unfollows-ex-girlfriend-on-x-after-she-shares-pics-with-new-boyfriend-5335375%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%20Unfollows%20Ex-Girlfriend%20On%20X%20After%20She%20Shares%20Pics%20With%20New%20Boyfriend%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Harris%20said%20that%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bstruggling%20to%20breathe%26quot%3B%20and%20thought%20she%20was%20going%20to%20die.%20%26quot%3BMy%20body%20was%20covered%20in%20hives.%20I%20felt%20like%20my%20skin%20was%20burning%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20recalled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20they%20gave%20me%20the%20adrenaline%2C%20it%20opened%20up%20my%20airways%20and%20my%20breathing%20improved.%20But%20my%20face%20was%20swollen%20for%20days%20after.%20I%20was%20really%20worried%20my%20face%20wouldn't%20go%20down.%20I%20didn't%20go%20out%20of%20the%20house%20for%20three%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Harris%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20doctors%2C%20Ms%20Harris'%20reaction%20to%20getting%20lip%20filler%20dissolved%20was%20due%20to%20an%20allergic%20reaction%20to%20hyaluronidase%20-%20a%20soluble%20protein%20enzyme%20which%20is%20often%20used%20by%20aestheticians%20to%20break%20down%20the%20hyaluronic%20acid%20found%20in%20lip%20filler.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711733100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fh5dtd2fg_lip-filler-generic_625x300_29_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fuk-woman-24-left-gasping-for-air-after-getting-lip-filler-dissolved-5335884%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2024-year-old%20woman%20in%