f%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F251019%2Fwildlife-rescue-kashmir-woman-teacher-leopard-bear-aaliya-mir-math-teacher-animal-human-conflict-yos191%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleopards%E2%80%99%20habitats%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20be%20destroyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%2C%20along%20with%20a%20few%20locals%2C%20and%20with%20the%20help%20and%20support%20of%20the%20Rajasthan%20Forest%20Department%20led%20by%20then%20DFO%20(Divisional%20Forest%20Officer)%20of%20Pali%20%E2%80%94%20IFS%20Balaji%20Kari%20%E2%80%94%20put%20their%20heads%20together%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20stop%20this%20from%20snowballing%20into%20a%20catastrophe.%20But%20as%20they%20would%20soon%20discover%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20that%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20spent%20the%20majority%20of%20three%20years%20having%20countless%20meetings%20with%20government%20officials%2C%20bureaucrats%20and%20ministers%20where%20he%20convinced%20the%20room%20that%20Jawai%20was%20the%20natural%20habitat%20of%20leopards%2C%20and%20that%20the%20area%20housed%20tremendous%20tourism%20potential.%20In%202014%2C%20the%20Government%20gave%20a%20premature%20termination%20notice%20to%20all%20the%20mines.%20The%20activity%20was%20soon%20discontinued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%2C%20who%20had%20quit%20a%20lucrative%20job%20in%20winemaking%20to%20turn%20his%20attention%20to%20the%20matter%2C%20now%20had%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F179096%2Fifs-officer-hero-mumbai-leopard-human-conflict-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20new%20dream%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20envisioned%20that%20the%20land%20that%20he%20had%20fought%20so%20hard%20to%20protect%20would%20now%20be%20a%20safe%20haven%20for%20the%20leopards%20and%20those%20who%20loved%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20Bera%20Safari%20Lodge%20stands%20on%20eight%20acres%20of%20land%20and%20is%20a%20gold%20standard%20in%20how%20luxury%20does%20not%20need%20to%20be%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20success%20story%20in%20conservation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%2C%20who%20is%20now%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20a%20successful%20boutique%20lodge%2C%20recalls%20his%20early%20days%20of%20renting%20out%20a%20room%20in%20his%20driver%E2%80%99s%20home.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20at%20the%20same%20time%20that%20I%20was%20fighting%20against%20the%20mining%20in%20the%20area.%20I%20had%20to%20stay%20on-site%2C%20so%20I%20lived%20with%20my%20driver%20who%20was%20a%20local%20in%20Bera.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20lot%20of%20criticism.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20used%20to%20make%20fun%20of%20me%20saying%20that%20I%20was%20living%20with%20my%20driver.%20But%20someone%20had%20to%20fight%20the%20mining%20project%20and%20I%20was%20very%20passionate%20about%20it.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F36889%2Finternational-day-of-snow-leopard%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20agenda%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20very%20clear.%20I%20thought%2C%20if%20nobody%20does%20it%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20doing%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20observation%20on%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20part%20has%20been%20the%20attitude%20of%20the%20locals%20towards%20the%20leopards.%20Once%20frightened%20about%20leopard%20attacks%2C%20he%20says%20the%20locals%20(aside%20from%20the%20Rabari%20community)%20would%20poison%20the%20beasts.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20today%2C%20due%20to%20the%20tourism%20model%20in%20Bera%2C%20every%20villager%20is%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20associated%20with%20it.%20Since%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20tourism%20here%20is%20safaris%20to%20see%20the%20leopard%2C%20they%20understand%20how%20important%20the%20animal%20is%20for%20their%20welfare.%20Today%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F12694%2Fvanamitra-suresh-conserve-wildlife-india-leopards%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehumans%20and%20leopards%20coexist%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconservation-1-1710483355.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Bera%20Safari%20Lodge%20has%20seven%20eco%20friendly%20cottages%20where%20people%20can%20stay%20along%20with%20safaris%20where%20guests%20can%20enjoy%20spotting%20the%20leopards%20and%20hyenas%20in%20the%20wild%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconservation-1-1710483355.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconservation-1-1710483355-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconservation-1-1710483355-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconservation-1-1710483355-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconservation-1-1710483355-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344905%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Bera%20Safari%20Lodge%20has%20seven%20eco%20friendly%20cottages%20where%20people%20can%20stay%20along%20with%20safaris%20where%20guests%20can%20enjoy%20spotting%20the%20leopards%20and%20hyenas%20in%20the%20wild%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Singh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%2C%20himself%20is%20fond%20of%20the%20wild%20cats.%20Calling%20himself%20a%20filmmaker%20conservationist%2C%20he%20lists%20the%20documentaries%20that%20he%20has%20covered%20featuring%20the%20wild%2C%20elaborates%20on%20a%20book%20%E2%80%98Leopards%20%26amp%3B%20Shepherds%20of%20JAWAI%E2%80%99%20that%20he%20co-authored%2C%20and%20casually%20mentions%20he%20was%20the%20cameraman%20on%20National%20Geographic%E2%80%99s%20special%20programme%20%E2%80%98Wild%20Cats%20of%20India%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20stints%20are%20illustrious.%20But%20ask%20him%20what%20he%20holds%20most%20dear%20to%20himself%2C%20and%20he%20says%20it%20is%20the%20memory%20of%20his%20first%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F166552%2Fpune-farmer-innovation-water-leopard%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleopard%20sighting%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CHer%20name%20was%20Zara%20and%20she%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20shy%20to%20be%20photographed%20at%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20used%20to%20come%20really%20close.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFear%20was%20the%20last%20thing%20on%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20mind.%20He%20understood%20the%20wild%20and%20it%20understood%20him%20back.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20is%20these%20learnings%20that%20he%20shares%20with%20his%20guests%20on%20the%20safari%20rides%20at%20Bera%20Safari%20Lodge.%20He%20urges%20people%20to%20revel%20in%20the%20beauty%20of%20watching%20leopards%20and%20humans%20live%20together%20here%20but%20cautions%20that%20this%20is%20not%20a%20national%20park.%20%E2%80%9CYou%E2%80%99ll%20see%20how%20wonderful%20it%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20adding%20that%20in%20over%20decades%20there%20has%20been%20zero%20human-animal%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20years%20when%20Singh%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20documenting%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fmeet-the-ladakhis-who-helped-save-indias-snow-leopards-with-innovative-ideas%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20wild%20cats%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20was%20building%20his%20dream%20homestay%20that%20started%20with%20three%20rooms%20and%20has%20now%20grown%20to%20seven.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stone%20construction%20is%20a%20paradise%20and%20is%20managed%20by%20staff%20from%20the%20region.%20The%20produce%20too%20is%20sourced%20from%20the%20village%2C%20and%20thus%2C%20Singh%20notes%20how%20they%20are%20part%20of%20the%20economy%20supporting%20local%20people.%20%E2%80%9COur%20main%20motto%20is%3A%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20sell%20rooms%2C%20we%20sell%20experiences%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20emphasises%20going%20on%20to%20add%20that%20their%20no%20TV%20policy%20is%20an%20extension%20of%20this.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20guests%20to%20be%20outside%20the%20room%20and%20enjoy%20nature.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335727%2Fintach-bengaluru-convenor-meera-iyer-restoring-forgotten-heritage-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20beauty%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20enjoyed.%20Sloth%20bears%2C%20hyenas%2C%20chinkaras%2C%20and%20various%20migratory%20bird%20species%20are%20what%20you%E2%80%99ll%20be%20spotting%20through%20your%20binoculars.%20Compliment%20Singh%20on%20the%20paradise%20he%20has%20created%20and%20the%20iconic%20journey%20he%20has%20had%2C%20and%20he%20smiles%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20simply%20my%20love%20for%20the%20wild%20that%20got%20me%20all%20the%20way%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pictures%20he%20has%20captured%20are%20as%20compelling%20as%20the%20journey.%20Here%20are%20some%20of%20them%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconservation-2-1710483596.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20leopards%20of%20Jawai%20as%20captured%20by%20Shatrunjay%20Pratap%20Singh%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconservation-2-1710483596.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconservati