%3EComing%20from%20an%20agricultural%20background%2C%20Kanchan%20turned%20to%20farming%20soon%20after%20her%20marriage.%20Alongside%20cultivating%20vegetables%2C%20wheat%2C%20and%20maize%2C%20the%20BA%20graduate%20sowed%20turmeric%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20programme%20on%20television%20that%20showcased%20the%20advantages%20of%20taking%20up%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F274975%2Fdivine-foods-helps-organic-turmeric-farmers-earn-double-sell-to-us-uk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eturmeric%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20learn%20more%20about%20it%2C%20I%20went%20to%20the%20nearby%20KVK%20(Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendra)%20and%20undertook%20a%20training%20programme%20of%20seven%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanchan%20opted%20for%20the%20Sangli%20variety%20of%20turmeric%20which%20has%20high%20curcumin%20turmeric%20and%20is%20often%20used%20for%20medicinal%20purposes.%20In%20addition%20to%20its%20deep-orange%20colour%20and%20rich%20aroma%2C%20Kanchan%20says%2C%20this%20variety%20produces%20big%20roots%20compared%20to%20other%20indigenous%20varieties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20procured%20eight%20quintals%20of%20%3Cem%3Ekachhi%20haldi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(seed)%20from%20KVK%20at%20Rs%2040%20per%20kg.%20%E2%80%9CThereafter%2C%20we%20started%20tilling%20the%20farmland%20to%20remove%20weeds%20and%20reduce%20the%20soil%20compaction%20%5Brelieve%20the%20tightness%20of%20soil%5D%2C%20and%20level%20the%20soil.%20After%20seedbed%20preparation%2C%20we%20added%20four%20trolleys%20(1%20trolley%20comprises%2040%20quintals)%20of%20cow%20dung%20in%20the%20soil.%20We%20then%20sowed%20germinated%20%3Cem%3Ekachhi%20haldi%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20the%20beds.%20The%20process%20is%20similar%20to%20sowing%20any%20tuber%20crop%20like%20potatoes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%