-kitchen-janta-dairy-sweets-mumbai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20the%20brothers%20reunited%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20decided%20not%20to%20go%20back%20to%20either%20London%20or%20Dubai%20and%20instead%20stay%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20to%20always%20discuss%20how%2C%20if%20we%20ever%20became%20business%20persons%2C%20we%20would%20enter%20the%20food%20industry.%20However%2C%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20passion%20towards%20having%20a%20farm%20motivated%20us%20to%20try%20our%20hand%20at%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20brothers%E2%80%99%20decision%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F320228%2Fpune-brothers-quit-job-to-start-organic-farming-venture-worth-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecome%20farmers%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20not%20well-received%20by%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20uncommon%20in%20Indian%20households%20for%20the%20relatives%20to%20have%20strong%20opinions.%20My%20father%20was%20told%20that%20he%20has%20put%20so%20much%20money%20into%20our%20education%20and%20sent%20us%20abroad%20for%20nothing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisheartened%20by%20the%20reaction%2C%20it%20was%20his%20father%20that%20gave%20them%20the%20courage.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20told%20us%20that%20we%20need%20not%20listen%20to%20anyone.%20If%20this%20feels%20right%2C%20then%20we%20must%20continue%20with%20the%20idea%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20nod%20from%20his%20parents%2C%20the%20brother%20duo%20decided%20to%20use%20some%20savings%20and%20loan%20some%20amount%20to%20set%20up%20the%20polyhouse%20farm%20in%20Agra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOrganic%2C%20natural%20and%20fresh%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%202020%2C%20the%20duo%20had%20initiated%20the%20setup%20of%20their%20farm.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20even%20secured%20a%2040%20percent%20government%20subsidy%2C%20prompting%20us%20to%20commence%20with%20planting%20English%20Cucumber%20in%20our%20polyhouse%20farm%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20four%20months%2C%20the%20duo%20established%20their%20initial%20cultivation%20and%20harvested%20it%20within%20five%20months.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20cucumber%20marked%20just%20the%20beginning.%20We%20sought%20further%20expansion%20and%20ventured%20into%20experimenting%20with%20additional%20vegetables%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20Ayush%20recalls%2C%20while%20he%20was%20in%20Delhi%2C%20he%20launched%20a%20small%20mushroom%20business.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20sourced%20mushrooms%20from%20farmers%2C%20packed%20them%2C%20and%20sold%20them.%20Although%20brief%2C%20it%20made%20me%20realise%20the%20substantial%20profit%20potential%20of%20mushrooms.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-2-1710404232.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22It%20was%20Ayush%20and%20Rishabh%20father's%20wish%20to%20start%20a%20polyhouse%20farm.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-2-1710404232.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-2-1710404232-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-2-1710404232-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-2-1710404232-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-2-1710404232-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344844%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIt%20was%20Ayush%20and%20Rishabh