22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cognifit.com%2Fassessment-scientific-validation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECognifit%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20a%20scientifically%20validated%20and%20leading%20brain%20training%20and%20cognitive%20assessments%20company%20%E2%80%94%20to%20provide%20a%20starting%20point%20for%20tests.%20Their%20battery%20of%20tests%20have%20been%20developed%20with%20more%20than%2020%20years%20of%20inputs%20and%20research%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20as%20Issac%20goes%20on%20to%20explain%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20cognitive%20test%20is%20just%20one%20of%20the%20many%20inputs%20which%20go%20into%20assessing%20someone%E2%80%99s%20cognitive%20decline%2C%20as%20every%20user%20is%20unique%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20cultural%20and%20sociological%20background.%20These%20assessments%20provide%20a%20cognitive%20report%20across%20various%20skills%2C%20and%20post%20that%2C%20more%20focussed%20assessments%20are%20carried%20out.%20Hence%2C%20every%20report%20that%20goes%20to%20the%20user%20is%20combined%20with%20a%20human%20interaction%20with%20a%20neuro%20counsellor%20to%20give%20a%20holistic%20risk%20assessment.%20Neuropsychologists%20then%20use%20these%20reports%20in%20consonance%20with%20their%20subjective%20examination%20of%20the%20patient%20to%20propose%20alternative%20lifestyle-based%20interventions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20neuropsychologist%20does%20employ%20a%20third-party%20assessment%20mechanism%20like%20a%20Mini-Mental%20State%20Examination%20(MMSE)%2C%20or%20a%20Montreal%20Cognitive%20Assessment%20(MoCA)%2C%20or%20an%20ICMR%20(Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research)-NCTB%20(Neuro%20Cognitive%20Tool%20Box)%2C%20or%20Addenbrooke%E2%80%99s%20Cognitive%20Examination%20(ACE)-III%20test.%20It%20is%20the%20combination%20of%20the%20test%20used%20along%20with%20a%20subjective%20interpretation%20and%20continuous%20tracking%20that%20makes%20for%20a%20more%20definitive%20assessment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20these%20cognitive%20and%20neuro-psychological%20assessments%2C%20counsellors%20hired%20by%20the%20startup%20suggest%20the%20next%20course%20of%20action%20which%20could%20include%20further%20clinical%20assessments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Rahul%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20proactive%20users%2C%20who%20would%20just%20want%20to%20ensure%20they%20are%20keeping%20themselves%20mentally%20active%20and%20take%20a%20preventive%20approach%20towards%20brain%20health%2C%20we%20have%20our%20app%20which%20offers%20daily%20quizzes%2C%20brain%20games%2C%20and%20daily%20tips%20for%20an%20active%20lifestyle%20leading%20to%20reduced%20impairment%20risk.%20We%20have%20also%20developed%20a%20personalised%20brain%20workout%20daily%2C%20calibrated%20to%20improve%20the%20skills%20they%20lag%20in.%20The%20daily%20workout%20currently%20consists%20of%202%20games%20and%20a%20mini-assessment%20to%20measure%20progress.%20Going%20ahead%20we%20will%20be%20developing%20our%20proprietary%20workouts%20as%20we%20understand%20more%20about%20these%20users.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDepending%20on%20how%20the%20user%20performs%2C%20either%20the%20difficulty%20level%20or%20the%20games%20are%20then%20changed%20on%20an%20ongoing%20basis.%20The%20user%20will%20also%20get%20charts%20of%20progress%20that%20they%20can%20see%20across%20the%20skills%20he%20is%20being%20tested%20for%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20A%20good%20starting%20point%20for%20this%20is%20the%20current%20cognitive%20age%20test%20that%20they%20have%20live%20that%20can%20be%20accessed%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapp.liveivory.com%2Fcognitive-age%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%20on%20mobile%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20daily%20tips%20they%20offer%20are%20live%20on%20their%20social%20media%20pages%2C%20which%20can%20be%20accessed%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%