want%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20youth%2C%20we%20want%20to%20give%20them%20the%20best%20design%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20youth%20knows%20what%20they%20want%20from%20the%20vehicle%20but%20also%20they%20want%20it%20to%20have%20some%20personality.%20So%20this%20became%20our%20driving%20force%2C%20we%20combine%20utility%20with%20design%20to%20create%20a%20product%20that%20is%20eco-friendly%20and%20suits%20our%20users.%20Just%20as%20a%20farmer%20drives%20his%20truck%20or%20tractor%20with%20pride%2C%20we%20want%20a%20small%20entrepreneur%2C%20say%20a%20carpenter%2C%20to%20have%20pride%20in%20driving%20his%20business%20vehicle%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scooter%20has%20the%20largest%20storage%20capacity%20of%2055%20litre%20which%20is%20three%20times%20more%20than%20the%20average%20scooter%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20have%20the%20largest%20floor%20board%20since%20people%20utilise%20every%20inch%20of%20the%20vehicle%20in%20India.%20You%20will%20often%20see%20grocery%20bags%2C%20school%20bags%2C%20and%20even%20kids%20standing%20on%20them.%20So%20in%20our%20product%2C%20we%20have%20included%20%E2%80%98Lock%20and%20Load%20Pannier%20Mounts%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20are%20sturdy%20alloy%20mounts%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20scooter.%20Attach%20pannier%20boxes%2C%20load%20up%20and%20make%20the%20most%20of%20the%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20love%20the%20hustle%20culture%20of%20our%20youth%20and%20we%20have%20made%20a%20vehicle%20designed%20especially%20for%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vehicle%20also%20has%20a%2012-litre%20lockable%20glove%20box%20with%20a%20USB%20charger.%20%E2%80%9CStore%20and%20lock%20up%20your%20valuables%20for%20safety%2C%20and%20easily%20access%20them%20while%20being%20seated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20range%20anxiety%20that%20most%20people%20deal%20with%2C%20he%20says%2C%